{"type":"message","id":"a51c8e42","parentId":"a5839b9f","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:12.418Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-23 04:03:11 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0 [msg:om_x100b5330e13fc4a0b32a2770deaaf69]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5330e13fc4a0b32a2770deaaf69\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-23 04:03 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\"\n}\n```\n\n你再增加一个定时任务，交易日的早上8点25分30秒开始筛选出符合竞价模式的个股，给出预测的成功率"}],"timestamp":1774209792415}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f845153","parentId":"a51c8e42","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:17.905Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求增加一个定时任务，在交易日的早上8点25分30秒筛选符合竞价模式的个股，并给出预测的成功率。\n\n首先我需要：\n1. 了解现有的定时任务情况\n2. 了解\"竞价模式\"是什么意思 - 可能需要查看memory或相关文件\n3. 创建这个cron任务\n\n让我先查看现有的cron任务和memory文件。","thinkingSignature":"b14e3422818a56ac18029e5807d8271977c76815351df1514e2d34942bdf102b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d28atxrmlg8r_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d28atxrmlg8r_2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"竞价模式 个股筛选 交易系统"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":139,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":313,"totalTokens":30461,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774209792417}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f00d0cb","parentId":"8f845153","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:17.954Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d28atxrmlg8r_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"03ab253b-2906-4537-bb8a-50d79929a2e1\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n      \"name\": \"A股每日竞价复盘\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774178531556,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774201816343,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 22 * * 1-5\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"执行A股超短每日复盘系统 v3.2（重构版）。\\n\\n步骤：\\n1. 确定今日日期 YYYYMMDD（如果今天是2026-03-23，则日期=20260323）\\n2. 确定昨日日期（上一个交易日，如果今天是周一，则上周五=20260320）\\n3. 运行今日预测：python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/main.py predict {今日日期}\\n4. 运行昨日追踪：python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/main.py outcome {昨日日期}\\n5. 获取准确率报告：python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/main.py accuracy\\n6. 生成飞书报告，格式如下：\\n\\n【今日涨停股预测】日期：YYYYMMDD\\n市场情绪：[从输出读取 phase_name/涨停均/炸板率]\\n预测股票数：X只\\n晋级分布：X只>30% / X只15-30% / X只<15%\\n板块效应：[最多3个联动板块]\\n\\n【重点关注】晋级概率>20%\\n[列出每只：代码/名称/板/晋级%/续涨分布/信号]\\n\\n【昨日预测复盘】日期：YYYYMMDD\\n实际晋级：X/X=XX%  续涨：X只(X%)  断板：X只(X%)\\n准确率：XX%（共X只，正确X只，错误X只）\\n[列出每只：代码/名称/板/晋级%/判断/实际结局]\\n\\n【概率标定】\\n[从accuracy输出读取各桶的预测均值vs实际率偏差]\\n[显示置信度标注]\\n\\n7. 将报告发送到飞书（你的飞书ID: ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0），标题「📊 A股每日复盘 YYYYMMDD」\\n\\n注意：\\n- 使用 BaoStock 获取K线数据（稳定不限流）\\n- 如果明日是周末，今日预测仍正常运行（outcome跳过）\\n- 如果今日是周一，运行 outcome 上周五\\n- 用message工具发送飞书消息到 user:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774274400000\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 1,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 1,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"03ab253b-2906-4537-bb8a-50d79929a2e1","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0","name":"A股每日竞价复盘","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774178531556,"updatedAtMs":1774201816343,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 22 * * 1-5","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行A股超短每日复盘系统 v3.2（重构版）。\n\n步骤：\n1. 确定今日日期 YYYYMMDD（如果今天是2026-03-23，则日期=20260323）\n2. 确定昨日日期（上一个交易日，如果今天是周一，则上周五=20260320）\n3. 运行今日预测：python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/main.py predict {今日日期}\n4. 运行昨日追踪：python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/main.py outcome {昨日日期}\n5. 获取准确率报告：python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/main.py accuracy\n6. 生成飞书报告，格式如下：\n\n【今日涨停股预测】日期：YYYYMMDD\n市场情绪：[从输出读取 phase_name/涨停均/炸板率]\n预测股票数：X只\n晋级分布：X只>30% / X只15-30% / X只<15%\n板块效应：[最多3个联动板块]\n\n【重点关注】晋级概率>20%\n[列出每只：代码/名称/板/晋级%/续涨分布/信号]\n\n【昨日预测复盘】日期：YYYYMMDD\n实际晋级：X/X=XX%  续涨：X只(X%)  断板：X只(X%)\n准确率：XX%（共X只，正确X只，错误X只）\n[列出每只：代码/名称/板/晋级%/判断/实际结局]\n\n【概率标定】\n[从accuracy输出读取各桶的预测均值vs实际率偏差]\n[显示置信度标注]\n\n7. 将报告发送到飞书（你的飞书ID: ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0），标题「📊 A股每日复盘 YYYYMMDD」\n\n注意：\n- 使用 BaoStock 获取K线数据（稳定不限流）\n- 如果明日是周末，今日预测仍正常运行（outcome跳过）\n- 如果今日是周一，运行 outcome 上周五\n- 用message工具发送飞书消息到 user:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774274400000}}],"total":1,"offset":0,"limit":1,"hasMore":false,"nextOffset":null},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774209797932}}
