{"type":"message","id":"904cf8ff","parentId":"69fa4570","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:21.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经有一个\"A股每日竞价复盘\"的定时任务在运行。现在用户要增加一个新的定时任务：交易日的早上8点25分30秒开始筛选符合竞价模式的个股。\n\n我需要：\n1. 了解竞价模式的具体定义和筛选逻辑 - 可能需要查看astock目录下的代码\n2. 创建一个新的cron任务\n\n让我先看看astock目录下的代码，了解竞价模式的筛选逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"296e072b08b49f741acca0f0ef12afb9947a04438ec020eb96a6217b74d3defa"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1lg9vg9oigmc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1418,"output":125,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31424,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774209797991}}
{"type":"message","id":"82497452","parentId":"904cf8ff","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:21.358Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1lg9vg9oigmc_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 116\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 gem gem  4096 Mar 23 03:30 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 8 gem gem  4096 Mar 23 01:38 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem 11120 Mar 23 03:39 analyze.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem   554 Mar 23 01:40 auction.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  3809 Mar 23 03:30 backfill_from_kline.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  5494 Mar 23 02:46 backfill.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  4168 Mar 23 01:40 calibration.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  1871 Mar 23 01:38 config.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  5397 Mar 23 02:30 db.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  1400 Mar 23 01:40 exit_signals.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  5819 Mar 23 03:40 fetch_kline.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  3497 Mar 23 02:18 formatter.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem   110 Mar 23 01:42 __init__.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  4293 Mar 23 01:48 kline.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem 11977 Mar 23 02:57 main.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  2400 Mar 23 02:17 market_data.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  3532 Mar 23 01:49 market.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  4356 Mar 23 01:40 predict.py\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 gem gem  4096 Mar 23 03:40 __pycache__"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"total 116\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 gem gem  4096 Mar 23 03:30 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 8 gem gem  4096 Mar 23 01:38 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem 11120 Mar 23 03:39 analyze.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem   554 Mar 23 01:40 auction.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  3809 Mar 23 03:30 backfill_from_kline.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  5494 Mar 23 02:46 backfill.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  4168 Mar 23 01:40 calibration.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  1871 Mar 23 01:38 config.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  5397 Mar 23 02:30 db.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  1400 Mar 23 01:40 exit_signals.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  5819 Mar 23 03:40 fetch_kline.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  3497 Mar 23 02:18 formatter.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem   110 Mar 23 01:42 __init__.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  4293 Mar 23 01:48 kline.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem 11977 Mar 23 02:57 main.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  2400 Mar 23 02:17 market_data.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  3532 Mar 23 01:49 market.py\n-rw-r--r-- 1 gem gem  4356 Mar 23 01:40 predict.py\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 gem gem  4096 Mar 23 03:40 __pycache__","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774209801349}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7d763f1","parentId":"82497452","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:23.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我看看 auction.py 和 predict.py 来理解竞价模式的具体逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"697fa00d56dfb428c73be9ab94bcfbcbd2c23fac1ef197bad30918be1dfd9d65"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5eu5uwk71m4o_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/auction.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5eu5uwk71m4o_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/predict.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2022,"output":92,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31995,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774209801358}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd2d9afe","parentId":"e7d763f1","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:23.610Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5eu5uwk71m4o_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nastock.auction\n竞价条件判断\n\"\"\"\n\n\ndef auction_ok(code, name, lb, jb_prob, vr, sector_hot):\n    \"\"\"\n    生成竞价观察条件说明。\n    返回 (ok_min, ok_max, vol_req, warning)\n    \"\"\"\n    if lb >= 3:\n        return 1, 6, \"缩量/平量\", \"⚠️高板位：竞价>+6%砸盘，<1%情绪弱\"\n    if sector_hot:\n        return 3, 8, \"温和放量\", \"✅联动板块，情绪支持\"\n    if jb_prob > 20:\n        return 3, 7, \"成交>昨日20%\", \"✅标准条件\"\n    return 4, 7, \"明显放量\", \"⚠️晋级概率偏低，需竞价强劲\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774209803598}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a091077","parentId":"bd2d9afe","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:23.622Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5eu5uwk71m4o_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nastock.predict\n预测核心 - 晋级概率计算 + 信号生成\n\"\"\"\nfrom config import BASE_PROBS, DEFAULT_COEF, PHASE_BASE_DISCOUNT\n\n\ndef load_coef():\n    \"\"\"加载系数配置（可后续扩展为文件持久化）\"\"\"\n    return dict(DEFAULT_COEF)\n\n\ndef calc_adj(trend, vr, dif, macd_val, rsi_val, cur, ma20, ma60, lb, coef=None):\n    \"\"\"\n    计算综合调整系数。\n    所有因子相乘得到总系数。\n    \"\"\"\n    if coef is None:\n        coef = load_coef()\n\n    f = 1.0\n    f *= coef.get(trend, 1.0)\n\n    if vr is not None:\n        if vr < 0.5:\n            f *= coef.get('vr_<0.5', 1.0)\n        elif vr < 0.8:\n            f *= coef.get('vr_<0.8', 1.0)\n        elif vr < 1.0:\n            f *= coef.get('vr_<1.0', 1.0)\n        elif vr < 1.5:\n            f *= coef.get('vr_<1.5', 1.0)\n        else:\n            f *= coef.get('vr_>=1.5', 1.0)\n\n    if rsi_val is not None:\n        if rsi_val < 40:\n            f *= coef.get('rsi_<40', 1.0)\n        elif rsi_val < 50:\n            f *= coef.get('rsi_<50', 1.0)\n        elif rsi_val < 60:\n            f *= coef.get('rsi_<60', 1.0)\n        elif rsi_val < 70:\n            f *= coef.get('rsi_<70', 1.0)\n        else:\n            f *= coef.get('rsi_>=70', 1.0)\n\n    dif_de_cross = None\n    if dif is not None and macd_val is not None:\n        dif_de_cross = '底部金叉' if (dif > 0 and macd_val > 0) else ('顶部死叉' if (dif < 0 and macd_val < 0) else None)\n    if dif_de_cross:\n        f *= coef.get(dif_de_cross, 1.0)\n\n    if cur is not None and ma20 is not None:\n        f *= coef.get('ma20上方', 1.0) if cur > ma20 else coef.get('ma20下方', 1.0)\n\n    lb_key = {1: '首板', 2: '2板', 3: '3板', 4: '4板', 5: '5板+'}.get(lb, '首板')\n    f *= coef.get(lb_key, 1.0)\n\n    return max(0.1, min(f, 3.0))\n\n\ndef build_signal(kl):\n    \"\"\"从K线指标生成信号描述列表\"\"\"\n    signals = []\n    if kl.get('trend') == '上升通道':\n        signals.append('上升通道')\n    elif kl.get('trend') == '下降通道':\n        signals.append('下降通道')\n    if kl.get('rsi'):\n        if kl['rsi'] < 40:\n            signals.append('RSI超卖')\n        elif kl['rsi'] > 70:\n            signals.append('RSI超买')\n        elif kl['rsi'] < 50:\n            signals.append('RSI偏弱')\n    if kl.get('macd_state'):\n        signals.append(kl['macd_state'])\n    if kl.get('vol_status') in ('极度缩量', '温和缩量'):\n        signals.append('缩量')\n    if kl.get('vol_status') == '极度缩量':\n        signals.append('极度缩量')\n    if kl.get('price_vs_ma20') == 'MA20上方':\n        signals.append('MA20上方')\n    return signals\n\n\ndef calc_distribution(lb, adj):\n    \"\"\"\n    计算N板/N+1板/N+2板的晋级概率分布。\n    adj是综合调整系数。\n    \"\"\"\n    next_lb = min(lb + 1, 5)\n    next2_lb = min(lb + 2, 5)\n\n    base_next = BASE_PROBS.get(next_lb, 0.10)\n    base_next2 = BASE_PROBS.get(next2_lb, 0.05)\n\n    # 调整后概率（有上限）\n    p_continue = min(base_next * adj * 0.7, 0.80)\n    p_jb = base_next * adj\n    p_jb = min(p_jb, 0.70)\n\n    return {\n        1: round((1 - p_jb) * 100, 1),\n        2: round(p_jb * 50, 1),\n        3: round(p_jb * 30, 1),\n        4: round(p_jb * 15, 1),\n        5: round(p_jb * 5, 1),\n    }\n\n\ndef predict_stock(code, lb, kl, coef_override=None, phase=None):\n    \"\"\"\n    给定股票代码、连板数、K线数据，返回预测结果dict。\n    \"\"\"\n    coef = coef_override or load_coef()\n\n    cur = kl.get('last_close')\n    ma20 = kl.get('ma20')\n    ma60 = kl.get('ma60')\n    rsi_val = kl.get('rsi')\n    vr = kl.get('vr')\n    dif = kl.get('dif')\n    macd_val = kl.get('macd')\n\n    adj = calc_adj(\n        kl.get('trend', '震荡'), vr, dif, macd_val, rsi_val,\n        cur, ma20, ma60, lb, coef\n    )\n\n    base = BASE_PROBS.get(min(lb + 1, 5), 0.10)\n\n    # 情绪周期折扣\n    discount = 1.0\n    if phase:\n        discount = PHASE_BASE_DISCOUNT.get(phase, 1.0)\n\n    jb_prob = round(min(base * adj * discount, 0.70) * 100, 1)\n    dz_prob = round(min(base * adj * 0.5 * discount, 0.30) * 100, 1)\n\n    dist = calc_distribution(lb, adj)\n    signal = ', '.join(build_signal(kl))\n\n    return {\n        'jb_prob': jb_prob,\n        'dz_prob': dz_prob,\n        'base_prob': round(base * 100, 1),\n        'adj_factor': round(adj, 2),\n        'discount': discount,\n        'distribution': dist,\n        'signal': signal,\n    }\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774209803614}}
{"type":"message","id":"af7a9652","parentId":"4a091077","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:26.593Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我理解了竞价模式。让我看看 main.py 的 predict 命令是如何工作的，这样我可以创建一个类似的任务但针对竞价模式筛选。","thinkingSignature":"e2323adbcc43cde2e6401ca3e8b9a83787f885c6f6e311582281dddbc6fd6b51"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8qf8n3qyi4bk_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/main.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3741,"output":67,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774209803621}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7dcdc55","parentId":"af7a9652","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:26.609Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8qf8n3qyi4bk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nastock.main\nCLI入口 + 命令路由\n\"\"\"\nimport sys, json, sqlite3\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 导入各模块\nfrom config import DB_PATH, EXIT_RULES\nfrom market import date_from_str, today_str, next_trading_day, prev_trading_day\nfrom kline import get_kline, get_next_close\nfrom predict import predict_stock, load_coef\nfrom db import get_db, init_db, save_predictions, save_daily_stats, save_historical_zt\nfrom calibration import update_calibration, get_calibration_report, suggest_coef_adjustments\nfrom auction import auction_ok\nfrom exit_signals import eval_exit_signals\nfrom market_data import get_zt_pool, get_zbgc_pool, get_dtgc_pool, get_market_sentiment\nimport akshare as ak\n\n\n# ===================== 核心逻辑 =====================\n\ndef detect_market_phase(conn):\n    \"\"\"检测市场情绪周期\"\"\"\n    rows = conn.execute(\n        \"SELECT date, total_zt, zt_rate, dz_rate FROM daily_stats ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 5\"\n    ).fetchall()\n    if len(rows) < 2:\n        return '未知', '样本不足'\n\n    zt_trend = rows[0]['total_zt'] - rows[-1]['total_zt']\n    dz_avg = sum(r['dz_rate'] or 0 for r in rows[:3]) / min(3, len(rows))\n\n    if dz_avg > 30 or zt_trend < -10:\n        return '退潮', f'炸板率{dz_avg:.0f}%/涨停递减'\n    if rows[0]['total_zt'] < 30:\n        return '冰点', f'涨停仅{rows[0][\"total_zt\"]}只'\n    if zt_trend > 10:\n        return '启动', f'涨停逐日增加'\n    if dz_avg > 15:\n        return '发酵', f'炸板率{dz_avg:.0f}%'\n    return '稳定', '市场平稳'\n\n\ndef run_predict(date):\n    \"\"\"执行预测逻辑\"\"\"\n    print(f\"[正在获取 {date} 涨停数据...]\")\n\n    # 获取涨停池（含连板数） + 涨停原因\n    zt_df, reasons = get_zt_pool(date)\n    if zt_df is None or len(zt_df) == 0:\n        print(f\"获取涨停池失败\")\n        return None, None, None, None\n\n    # 获取炸板池、跌停池（市场情绪用）\n    try:\n        zbgc_df = get_zbgc_pool(date)\n        dt_df = get_dtgc_pool(date)\n        zt_count = len(zt_df)\n        zbgc_count = len(zbgc_df) if zbgc_df is not None else 0\n        dt_count = len(dt_df) if dt_df is not None else 0\n        total = zt_count + zbgc_count\n        zbgc_rate = round(zbgc_count / total * 100, 1) if total > 0 else 0\n        dt_rate = round(dt_count / (zt_count + dt_count) * 100, 1) if (zt_count + dt_count) > 0 else 0\n        sentiment = f\"涨停{zt_count}只 炸板{zbgc_count}只({zbgc_rate}%) 跌停{dt_count}只({dt_rate}%)\"\n    except Exception:\n        sentiment = \"获取情绪数据失败\"\n        zbgc_rate = 0\n\n    # 板块统计\n    sector_raw = {}\n    for _, r in zt_df.iterrows():\n        ind = str(r.get('行业', '其他'))\n        if ind not in sector_raw:\n            sector_raw[ind] = {'total': 0}\n        sector_raw[ind]['total'] += 1\n\n    conn = get_db()\n    phase, phase_name = detect_market_phase(conn)\n\n    results = []\n    for _, row in zt_df.iterrows():\n        code = str(row['代码']).zfill(6)\n        name = str(row.get('名称', code))\n        lb = int(row.get('连板数', 1) or 1)\n        industry = str(row.get('行业', '其他'))\n        reason = reasons.get(code, '')\n\n        kl = get_kline(code)\n        if kl is None:\n            continue\n\n        pred = predict_stock(code, lb, kl, phase=phase)\n        results.append({\n            'date': date, 'code': code, 'name': name,\n            'lb': lb, 'industry': industry,\n            'reason': reason,\n            'trend': kl.get('trend'), 'rsi': kl.get('rsi'), 'vr': kl.get('vr'),\n            'macd_state': kl.get('macd_state'), 'vol_status': kl.get('vol_status'),\n            'price_vs_ma20': kl.get('price_vs_ma20'),\n            'kline': kl,\n            'prediction': pred,\n        })\n\n    save_predictions(date, results, phase, phase_name)\n\n    # 保存当日涨停到历史表（自然积累，从今天开始）\n    hist_stocks = []\n    for r in results:\n        p = r.get('prediction', {})\n        kl_data = r.get('kline', {})\n        prev_close = kl_data.get('close', 0) / (1 + p.get('pct_chg', 0) / 100) if p.get('pct_chg', 0) != 0 else kl_data.get('close', 0)\n        is_cyb = r['code'].startswith(('300', '688', '301'))\n        zt_pct = 20.0 if is_cyb else 10.0\n        zt_price = round(prev_close * (1 + zt_pct / 100), 2) if prev_close else 0\n        hist_stocks.append({\n            'code': r['code'], 'name': r['name'],\n            'close': kl_data.get('close', 0),\n            'high': kl_data.get('high', 0),\n            'zt_price': zt_price,\n            'pct_chg': p.get('pct_chg', 0),\n            'turn_rate': 0,\n            'reason': r.get('reason', ''),\n            'industry': r.get('industry', ''),\n            'lb': r.get('lb', 1),\n        })\n    if hist_stocks:\n        # 统一日期格式为 YYYY-MM-DD\n        date_fmt = f\"{date[:4]}-{date[4:6]}-{date[6:8]}\"\n        save_historical_zt(date_fmt, hist_stocks)\n\n    avg_jb = sum(r['prediction']['jb_prob'] for r in results) / len(results) if results else 0\n    print(f\"[预测完成: {len(results)}只 | 情绪:{phase_name} | 均晋级概率:{avg_jb:.1f}%]\")\n    conn.close()\n    return results, phase, phase_name, sector_raw, sentiment\n\n\ndef run_outcome(date):\n    \"\"\"追踪T日预测的T+1实际结局\"\"\"\n    conn = get_db()\n    nd = next_trading_day(date)\n    print(f\"[T日 {date} → T+1日 {nd}]\")\n\n    try:\n        next_zt = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date=nd)\n        zt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date=date)\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"获取涨停池失败: {e}\")\n        return\n\n    codes21 = {str(r['代码']).zfill(6): int(r.get('连板数', 1) or 1) for _, r in next_zt.iterrows()}\n    codes20 = {str(r['代码']).zfill(6): int(r.get('连板数', 1) or 1) for _, r in zt_df.iterrows()}\n    in_next = set(codes21.keys())\n\n    rows = conn.execute(\"SELECT * FROM predictions WHERE date=?\", (date,)).fetchall()\n    jb_c = xux_c = duan_c = 0\n\n    for row in rows:\n        code = row['code']\n        lb21 = codes21.get(code, 0)\n        lb20 = row['lb'] or 1\n\n        if lb21 > lb20:\n            outcome = '晋级'\n            detail = f'{lb20}板→{lb21}板'\n            jb_c += 1\n        elif code not in in_next:\n            outcome = '断板'\n            detail = '未续涨'\n            duan_c += 1\n        else:\n            outcome = '续涨'\n            detail = f'维持{lb21}板'\n            xux_c += 1\n\n        conn.execute(\n            \"UPDATE predictions SET outcome=?,detail=?,actual_boards=? WHERE date=? AND code=?\",\n            (outcome, detail, lb21 if lb21 > 0 else None, date, code)\n        )\n\n    conn.commit()\n    update_calibration(conn)\n    conn.close()\n\n    total = len(rows)\n    print(f\"实际晋级: {jb_c}/{total}={jb_c/total*100:.1f}%  续涨:{xux_c}只({xux_c/total*100:.1f}%)  断板:{duan_c}只({duan_c/total*100:.1f}%)\")\n\n    return {\n        'jb': jb_c, '续涨': xux_c, '断板': duan_c, 'total': total,\n        'nd': nd, 'date': date\n    }\n\n\n# ===================== CLI命令 =====================\n\ndef cmd_predict(date):\n    ret = run_predict(date)\n    if ret[0] is None:\n        return\n    results, phase, phase_name, sector_raw, sentiment = ret\n\n    from formatter import fmt_predict_terminal, fmt_auction_mobile\n    print(fmt_predict_terminal(date, results, sector_raw, phase, phase_name, sentiment))\n    print()\n    print(fmt_auction_mobile(results, sector_raw))\n\n\ndef cmd_outcome(date):\n    result = run_outcome(date)\n    if not result:\n        return\n\n    conn = get_db()\n    rows = conn.execute(\n        \"SELECT * FROM predictions WHERE date=? ORDER BY jb_prob DESC\", (date,)\n    ).fetchall()\n\n    print(f\"\\n{'=' * 60}\\n  追踪结局 {date}\\n{'=' * 60}\")\n    print(f\"{'代码':<8}{'名称':<10}{'板':<4}{'晋级%':<7}{'判断':<6}{'实际'}\")\n    print('-' * 50)\n    for row in rows:\n        jb_p = row['jb_prob']\n        correct = (row['outcome'] == '晋级' and jb_p > 50) or (row['outcome'] != '晋级' and jb_p <= 50)\n        icon = '✅' if correct else '⚠️'\n        detail = row['detail'] or row['outcome'] or ''\n        print(f\"{row['code']:<8}{row['name'][:8]:<10}{row['lb']:<4}板 {jb_p:<6.1f}% {icon}  {detail}\")\n    conn.close()\n\n\ndef cmd_accuracy():\n    conn = get_db()\n    report = get_calibration_report(conn)\n    if report:\n        print(f\"\\n{'=' * 50}\\n  概率标定报告\\n{'=' * 50}\\n{report}\")\n    else:\n        print(\"样本不足，等待更多数据积累后查看标定报告。\")\n    conn.close()\n\n\ndef cmd_positions(all_flag=False):\n    conn = get_db()\n    if all_flag:\n        rows = conn.execute(\"SELECT * FROM positions ORDER BY created_at DESC\").fetchall()\n        label = \"全部持仓\"\n    else:\n        rows = conn.execute(\"SELECT * FROM positions WHERE status='持仓' ORDER BY created_at DESC\").fetchall()\n        label = \"当前持仓\"\n\n    if not rows:\n        print(f\"暂无{'活跃' if not all_flag else ''}持仓记录。\")\n        conn.close()\n        return\n\n    exits = eval_exit_signals(conn)\n\n    print(f\"\\n{'=' * 60}\\n  {label}\\n{'=' * 60}\")\n    print(f\"{'代码':<8}{'名称':<10}{'买入日':<10}{'买入价':<10}{'现价':<10}{'浮盈%':<10}{'持仓天':<8}{'状态'}\")\n    print('-' * 70)\n    for r in rows:\n        print(f\"{r['code']:<8}{r['name']:<10}{r['buy_date']:<10}{r['buy_price']:<10.2f}\"\n              f\"{r['cur_price']:<10.2f}{r['profit_pct']:<10.1f}{r['hold_days']:<8}{r['status']}\")\n\n    if exits:\n        print(f\"\\n{'=' * 60}\\n  卖出信号\\n{'=' * 60}\")\n        for e in exits:\n            if e['signal']:\n                print(f\"  {e['name']}({e['code']}): {e['signal']}\")\n    conn.close()\n\n\ndef cmd_buy(date, code, buy_price):\n    conn = get_db()\n    name = code  # 简化，可通过接口查询名称\n    cur_p = get_next_close(code) or float(buy_price)\n    profit_pct = 0.0\n\n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        INSERT INTO positions (code, name, buy_date, buy_price, cur_price, profit_pct, hold_days, status)\n        VALUES (?,?,?,?,?,?,0,'持仓')\n    \"\"\", (code, name, date, float(buy_price), cur_p, profit_pct))\n    conn.commit()\n    conn.close()\n    print(f\"已记录买入: {code} {name} @ {buy_price} ({date})\")\n\n\ndef cmd_sell(code):\n    conn = get_db()\n    conn.execute(\"UPDATE positions SET status='已卖出' WHERE code=? AND status='持仓'\", (code,))\n    conn.commit()\n    row = conn.execute(\"SELECT * FROM positions WHERE code=? ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1\", (code,)).fetchone()\n    profit = row['profit_pct'] if row else 0.0\n    conn.close()\n    print(f\"已卖出: {code}  浮盈: {profit:.1f}%\")\n\n\ndef cmd_apply_coef():\n    print(\"系数调整需人工确认后执行，暂不支持自动应用。\")\n\n\n# ===================== CLI路由 =====================\n\ndef main():\n    cmd = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else 'help'\n\n    if cmd == 'predict':\n        date = sys.argv[2] if len(sys.argv) > 2 else today_str()\n        cmd_predict(date)\n\n    elif cmd == 'outcome':\n        if len(sys.argv) < 3:\n            print(\"用法: outcome <日期>\"); return\n        cmd_outcome(sys.argv[2])\n\n    elif cmd == 'accuracy':\n        cmd_accuracy()\n\n    elif cmd == 'positions':\n        all_flag = (len(sys.argv) > 2 and sys.argv[2] == 'all')\n        cmd_positions(all_flag)\n\n    elif cmd == 'buy':\n        if len(sys.argv) < 5:\n            print(\"用法: buy <日期> <代码> <买入价>\"); return\n        cmd_buy(sys.argv[2], sys.argv[3], sys.argv[4])\n\n    elif cmd == 'sell':\n        if len(sys.argv) < 3:\n            print(\"用法: sell <代码>\"); return\n        cmd_sell(sys.argv[2])\n\n    elif cmd == 'init':\n        from db import init_db as _init\n        print(f\"数据库初始化完成: {_init()}\")\n\n    else:\n        print(f\"\"\"用法:\n  predict [日期]           - 预测+竞价自检\n  outcome <日期>           - 追踪结局\n  accuracy                 - 概率标定报告\n  positions [all]          - 查看持仓（加all看历史）\n  buy <日期> <代码> <买入价> - 记录买入\n  sell <代码>              - 卖出\n  init                     - 初始化数据库\"\"\")\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774209806601}}
{"type":"message","id":"72378a34","parentId":"e7dcdc55","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:29.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我理解了整个系统的结构。用户想要在交易日早上8:25:30进行竞价模式筛选，给出预测成功率。\n\n让我看看formatter.py里的fmt_auction_mobile函数，了解竞价输出的格式。","thinkingSignature":"bf1bd08428844c4dd6cdf98e1cee44685ba8e80dc4f8a98d03aaa436c5145794"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_km4q1ihrbcm3_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/formatter.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7346,"output":83,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37310,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774209806608}}
{"type":"message","id":"84e203d7","parentId":"72378a34","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:29.736Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_km4q1ihrbcm3_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nastock.formatter\n输出格式化 - 终端、飞书消息\n\"\"\"\n\n# ===================== 终端格式化 =====================\n\ndef fmt_predict_terminal(date, results, sector_raw, phase, phase_name, sentiment=''):\n    \"\"\"终端预测输出\"\"\"\n    lines = [\n        f\"{'=' * 60}\",\n        f\"  A股超短每日预测 v3.2  {date}\",\n        f\"{'=' * 60}\",\n        f\"\",\n        f\"市场情绪: {sentiment if sentiment else phase_name}  涨停股: {len(results)}只\",\n        f\"\",\n    ]\n\n    # 板块效应\n    if sector_raw:\n        sorted_sectors = sorted(sector_raw.items(), key=lambda x: x[1]['total'], reverse=True)\n        lines.append(\"  板块效应\")\n        lines.append(\"-\" * 40)\n        for ind, data in sorted_sectors:\n            n = data['total']\n            tag = '🚀板块联动' if n >= 3 else ('📌多股' if n == 2 else '')\n            lines.append(f\"  {ind[:12]:<12}{n:<6}{tag}\")\n        lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 晋级分布\n    gt30 = sum(1 for r in results if r['prediction']['jb_prob'] > 30)\n    gt15 = sum(1 for r in results if 15 < r['prediction']['jb_prob'] <= 30)\n    lt15 = len(results) - gt30 - gt15\n    lines.append(f\"晋级分布: >30%:{gt30}只 / 15-30%:{gt15}只 / <15%:{lt15}只\")\n    lines.append(\"\")\n\n    return '\\n'.join(lines)\n\n\ndef fmt_auction_mobile(results, sector_raw):\n    \"\"\"\n    手机易读格式：分行输出，每行一个标的。\n    \"\"\"\n    lines = [\"📋 明日竞价自检（重点6只）\\n\"]\n\n    for r in results[:6]:\n        p = r['prediction']\n        n = sector_raw.get(r['industry'], {}).get('total', 0)\n        sector_hot = (n >= 3)\n        from auction import auction_ok\n        ok_min, ok_max, vol, warn = auction_ok(\n            r['code'], r['name'], r['lb'], p['jb_prob'], r.get('vr'), sector_hot\n        )\n        sig = p['signal'].split(',')[0] if p['signal'] else ''\n        lines.append(f\"● {r['name']}({r['code']})\")\n        lines.append(f\"  {r['lb']}板 | 晋级{p['jb_prob']:.1f}% | 竞价{ok_min}~{ok_max}% | {vol}\")\n        reason = r.get('reason', '')\n        if reason:\n            lines.append(f\"  📌涨停原因: {reason}\")\n        lines.append(f\"  {warn} | {sig}\")\n        lines.append(\"\")\n\n    # 次级\n    others = [r for r in results[6:10]]\n    if others:\n        lines.append(\"📋 次级关注（按需参考）\\n\")\n        for r in others:\n            p = r['prediction']\n            n = sector_raw.get(r['industry'], {}).get('total', 0)\n            sector_hot = (n >= 3)\n            ok_min, ok_max, vol, warn = auction_ok(\n                r['code'], r['name'], r['lb'], p['jb_prob'], r.get('vr'), sector_hot\n            )\n            lines.append(f\"  {r['name']}({r['code']}) {r['lb']}板 竞价{ok_min}~{ok_max}% {vol}\")\n\n    return '\\n'.join(lines)\n\n\ndef fmt_positions(conn):\n    \"\"\"持仓格式化\"\"\"\n    rows = conn.execute(\n        \"SELECT * FROM positions WHERE status='持仓' ORDER BY created_at DESC\"\n    ).fetchall()\n    if not rows:\n        return \"暂无持仓记录。\"\n\n    lines = [\n        f\"{'=' * 60}\",\n        f\"  当前持仓\",\n        f\"{'=' * 60}\",\n        f\"{'代码':<8}{'名称':<10}{'买入日':<10}{'买入价':<10}{'现价':<10}{'浮盈%':<10}{'持仓天':<8}{'状态'}\",\n        f\"{'-' * 70}\",\n    ]\n    for r in rows:\n        lines.append(\n            f\"{r['code']:<8}{r['name']:<10}{r['buy_date']:<10}\"\n            f\"{r['buy_price']:<10.2f}{r['cur_price']:<10.2f}\"\n            f\"{r['profit_pct']:<10.1f}{r['hold_days']:<8}{r['status']}\"\n        )\n    return '\\n'.join(lines)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774209809728}}
{"type":"message","id":"e15bff18","parentId":"84e203d7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:03:53.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我有了完整的理解。用户想要一个定时任务，在交易日的早上8:25:30开始筛选符合竞价模式的个股，并给出预测的成功率。\n\n现有的\"A股每日竞价复盘\"任务是在收盘后（22:00）运行，调用的是`run_predict`，这是基于昨日涨停数据的复盘和预测。\n\n用户要的新任务是**当日**早上8:25:30运行，这时需要获取当日涨停数据（因为9:30开盘前就要做决策）。让我看看能不能直接从今日实时数据获取。\n\n实际上，在交易日的早上8:25:30（开盘前），当日涨停数据还没有，因为股票还没开始交易。所以这个任务应该是：\n- 从昨日涨停股票中筛选符合竞价模式的个股\n- 基于昨日数据预测成功率\n\n让我看看市场数据获取函数，了解能否获取前一日的数据。\n\n实际上，看代码中的`run_predict`是获取历史涨停数据（昨日收市后），而用户想要的是在开盘前来做这个筛选。所以应该是在8:25运行，获取前一日（已经是交易日）的涨停数据。\n\n现在我需要创建一个cron任务：\n- 时间：周一到周五 08:25:30 Asia/Shanghai\n- 触发一个agent任务，筛选符合竞价模式的个股并给出成功率预测\n\n\n- 任务流程包括获取前一个交易日（周五如果周一是周一）的涨停数据，然后筛选符合竞价模式的股票，计算预测成功率，最后生成飞书报告\n\n竞价模式的判断逻辑在`auction.py`中，我需要提取关键指标如连板数、竞价概率、量比和板块热度。\n\n对于cron表达式，工作日早上8:25应该是`30 25 8 * * 1-5`，但这条规则在周六和周日不会执行，所以我需要确认这个时间设置是否符合需求。","thinkingSignature":"459702562cf6526fb9196b2d15ee53d8ec75a281a5d455516f8741e9a9a1e08d"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了。我来创建一个交易日上午8:25:30的竞价模式筛选任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3hnhpu86i415_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"A股竞价模式筛选","schedule":{"expr":"30 25 8 * * 1-5","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行A股竞价模式筛选任务。\n\n背景：这是交易日早上8:25，开盘前筛选。\n\n步骤：\n1. 确定今日日期和前一交易日（如果是周一，则取上周五）。用以下Python获取：\n```python\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\ntoday = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n# 计算前一交易日\ntoday_dt = datetime.strptime(today, '%Y%m%d')\nif today_dt.weekday() == 0:  # 周一\n    prev_dt = today_dt - timedelta(days=3)  # 上周五\nelse:\n    prev_dt = today_dt - timedelta(days=1)\nprev_date = prev_dt.strftime('%Y%m%d')\n```\n\n2. 获取前一交易日涨停数据：\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\nzt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date='YYYYMMDD')  # 前一交易日的涨停股\n```\n\n3. 对涨停股逐只获取K线数据（用 BaoStock 或 akshare），计算：\n   - 连板数(lb)\n   - 量比(vr)\n   - RSI\n   - MACD状态\n   - 趋势\n   - MA20/MA60位置\n\n4. 使用 auction_ok 函数判断竞价条件：\n```python\nfrom auction import auction_ok\nok_min, ok_max, vol_req, warning = auction_ok(code, name, lb, jb_prob, vr, sector_hot)\n```\n\n5. 筛选出符合竞价模式的股票（ok_min <= 7 and vr >= 0.5）\n\n6. 计算预测晋级成功率分布（使用 predict_stock 函数）\n\n7. 生成飞书报告，格式如下：\n\n【📈 竞价模式筛选】日期：YYYYMMDD（前一交易日YYYYMMDD复盘）\n\n市场情绪：[从涨停数量、炸板率判断]\n筛选股票数：X只\n\n【✅ 重点竞价】\n| 股票 | 板位 | 晋级概率 | 竞价要求 | 量比 | 板块 |\n|------|------|----------|----------|------|------|\n| 代码/名称 | X板 | XX% | X~X% | X | XX |\n\n【晋级概率分布】\n- >30%：X只\n- 15-30%：X只  \n- <15%：X只\n\n【板块联动】（有板块效应的列出）\n- XX板块：X只\n\n【操作建议】\n- 激进型：XX（晋级概率>30%）\n- 稳健型：XX（15-30%区间）\n\n注意：这是竞价模式筛选，给出的是预测成功率，实际结果会受市场情绪影响。\n\n8. 用message工具发送到飞书（你的飞书ID: ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0），标题「🚀 竞价模式筛选 YYMMDD」","timeoutSeconds":600},"sessionTarget":"isolated","enabled":true}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8488,"output":1149,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774209809735}}
