15%：X只\\n\\n【板块联动】（有板块效应的列出）\\n- XX板块：X只\\n\\n【操作建议】\\n- 激进型：XX（晋级概率>30%）\\n- 稳健型：XX（15-30%区间）\\n\\n注意：这是竞价模式筛选，给出的是预测成功率，实际结果会受市场情绪影响。\\n\\n8. 用message工具发送到飞书（你的飞书ID: ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0），标题「🚀 竞价模式筛选 YYMMDD」\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"to\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774225530000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"dc676ffd-0c3d-470b-9a6d-93e3c01dfcc8","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0","name":"A股竞价模式筛选","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774209833478,"updatedAtMs":1774209833478,"schedule":{"expr":"30 25 8 * * 1-5","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行A股竞价模式筛选任务。\n\n背景：这是交易日早上8:25，开盘前筛选。\n\n步骤：\n1. 确定今日日期和前一交易日（如果是周一，则取上周五）。用以下Python获取：\n```python\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\ntoday = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n# 计算前一交易日\ntoday_dt = datetime.strptime(today, '%Y%m%d')\nif today_dt.weekday() == 0:  # 周一\n    prev_dt = today_dt - timedelta(days=3)  # 上周五\nelse:\n    prev_dt = today_dt - timedelta(days=1)\nprev_date = prev_dt.strftime('%Y%m%d')\n```\n\n2. 获取前一交易日涨停数据：\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\nzt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date='YYYYMMDD')  # 前一交易日的涨停股\n```\n\n3. 对涨停股逐只获取K线数据（用 BaoStock 或 akshare），计算：\n   - 连板数(lb)\n   - 量比(vr)\n   - RSI\n   - MACD状态\n   - 趋势\n   - MA20/MA60位置\n\n4. 使用 auction_ok 函数判断竞价条件：\n```python\nfrom auction import auction_ok\nok_min, ok_max, vol_req, warning = auction_ok(code, name, lb, jb_prob, vr, sector_hot)\n```\n\n5. 筛选出符合竞价模式的股票（ok_min <= 7 and vr >= 0.5）\n\n6. 计算预测晋级成功率分布（使用 predict_stock 函数）\n\n7. 生成飞书报告，格式如下：\n\n【📈 竞价模式筛选】日期：YYYYMMDD（前一交易日YYYYMMDD复盘）\n\n市场情绪：[从涨停数量、炸板率判断]\n筛选股票数：X只\n\n【✅ 重点竞价】\n| 股票 | 板位 | 晋级概率 | 竞价要求 | 量比 | 板块 |\n|------|------|----------|----------|------|------|\n| 代码/名称 | X板 | XX% | X~X% | X | 