{"type":"message","id":"c8dbda97","parentId":"35a8603c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:32:42.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the process is running. Let me check the log file after a few seconds to see if there's output.","thinkingSignature":"4e5af5c0457071ae3475404cc46b0b5aeedaee92199d922a857c8dc22df8c7f7"},{"type":"text","text":"已在后台跑起来了（PID 301485）。\n\n**配置：**\n- 断点续传：从第 1000 只继续\n- 自动重试：最多 3 次\n- 约 8600 只A股 remaining，预计要跑比较久\n- 日志实时写入 `/data/astock/kline/fetch.log`\n\n中途如果断了，下次自动从断点继续，不需要人工干预。我会在下次报告时告诉你进度。🦞"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20125,"output":118,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50124,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774211556598}}
{"type":"message","id":"12822f3a","parentId":"c8dbda97","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:37:31.708Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-23 04:37:31 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0 [msg:om_x100b53317e6438a8b2d7155977e7d6f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53317e6438a8b2d7155977e7d6f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-23 04:37 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\"\n}\n```\n\n要不要建立一个agent专门负责消息挖掘"}],"timestamp":1774211851704}}
{"type":"message","id":"c965c109","parentId":"12822f3a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:37:45.157Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if we should build a dedicated agent for message mining. Let me think about what this means in context.\n\nLooking at the astock system, we have:\n1. A trading system that does daily review (收盘复盘) at 22:00\n2. A new auction/filtering task at 08:25 for pre-market screening\n3. K-line data fetching running in background\n\nThe user might be asking about:\n1. A dedicated agent/sub-agent for mining Feishu messages (e.g., gathering market intelligence, sector info, trading ideas from group chats)\n2. Or a dedicated agent for the astock system itself\n\nGiven the context is about A-stock trading, I think they might be asking about:\n\n\n1. Mining stock-related messages from Feishu groups/channels for market sentiment, stock tips, sector news\n2. Or simply a dedicated agent to handle all the astock-related tasks (data collection, analysis, reports)\n\nI should clarify what they're thinking - is it about extracting market intelligence from Feishu conversations, or having a separate agent continuously running the trading system? The message mining could be valuable if there are group chats with relevant market discussions.","thinkingSignature":"0902a4c04990eb278d6503b9b06a40be5eb9d79decbd60959fcba210c17bd895"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题。两个方向，你想的是哪个？\n\n**1. 飞书消息挖掘**\n专门扫描群聊、频道里的关键词、情绪信号，辅助判断板块热点。比如有人在群里提了某个板块很火，可以作为市场情绪的补充数据源。\n\n**2. A股系统专用 Agent**\n把数据抓取、分析、复盘、竞价筛选这些任务打包成一个独立 Agent，24小时无人值守运行，不占用主会话资源。\n\n---\n\n我的判断：**第二个更值得做**。因为：\n- 消息挖掘的价值高度依赖群质量，不一定有那么高质量的信源\n- 现在这套系统已经跑起来了，配一个专属 Agent 负责监控数据流、定时任务、异常告警，效率更高\n\n你想先搞哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":397,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":20293,"totalTokens":50699,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774211851706}}
{"type":"message","id":"75e56ac9","parentId":"c965c109","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:40:23.803Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-23 04:40:23 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0 [msg:om_x100b533175a36ca0b2cedcc0435615f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b533175a36ca0b2cedcc0435615f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-23 04:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\"\n}\n```\n\n新建一个agent专门负责爬取财联社、淘股吧、同花顺、东方财富、雪球等财经媒体的新闻，负责消息的整理分析，配合你做股票分析，名字就叫狗仔"}],"timestamp":1774212023797}}
{"type":"message","id":"1bfe4754","parentId":"75e56ac9","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:40:34.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to create a new agent called \"狗仔\" (Gossip/Paparazzi) that specializes in crawling financial news from various sources like CLX (财联社), Taoguba (淘股吧), Tonghuashun (同花顺), Eastmoney (东方财富), and Xueqiu (雪球). This agent would be responsible for news collection, organization, and analysis to support stock analysis.\n\nI should create a new agent/sub-agent for this purpose. I need to:\n1. Create the agent with a proper configuration\n2. Set up crawling for these financial news sources\n3. Define what it should do with the collected news\n\nLet me think about the architecture:\n\n\n- This should be a persistent sub-agent that runs on a schedule to collect news\n- It should summarize and organize the news\n- It should push relevant news to the main agent or make it available for the main agent to use\n- The agent should be able to monitor specific stocks or sectors based on the main agent's requests\n\nFor the technical implementation, I need to set up RSS feeds or web scraping for each source—CLX has an RSS feed, while the others will require web scraping. I should create a dedicated agent configuration file for \"狗仔\" and a Python crawler that can handle multiple sources with deduplication, then configure the agent with the appropriate system prompt and scheduling.\n\nNow I'm checking the ClawHub skill to understand how agents are configured in OpenClaw.","thinkingSignature":"81717a9a90fcd9c1f0c9b1697a7702a136f9614a39e60e69443ee42fdb6de083"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_80ealyw1xclo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":341,"cacheRead":50001,"cacheWrite":650,"totalTokens":51120,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774212023801}}
{"type":"message","id":"6cd7c58b","parentId":"1bfe4754","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:40:34.942Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_80ealyw1xclo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774212034932}}
