{"type":"message","id":"11f9ef9e","parentId":"7927036e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:42:02.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the SKILL.md for the crawler, and then set up a cron job to run it periodically. But first, let me also create the AGENTS.md for the狗仔 workspace.","thinkingSignature":"1133d85b22d2a80e0174d440f724b30a2e075e84dc51e102d3f4efe489500f3f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g7xw0xl84vv4_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/AGENTS.md","content":"# AGENTS.md - 狗仔工作空间\n\n## 角色\n财经媒体爬虫 + 消息分析 Agent\n\n## 核心任务\n1. 每30分钟爬取一次五大财经媒体（财联社、东方财富、同花顺、雪球、淘股吧）\n2. 去重后存入数据库\n3. 提取热门股票关键词\n4. 生成简报推送给主人\n\n## 定时任务\n- 每30分钟爬取一次（7:00-22:00）\n- 每天9:30、13:00生成重点资讯简报\n\n## 依赖\n- Python: requests, bs4, fire\n- 数据目录: /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/data/\n\n## 关键脚本\n- scripts/crawler.py: 主爬虫，支持 run/recent/hot 子命令\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43001,"output":267,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73149,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774212114731}}
