{"type":"message","id":"e1781b28","parentId":"32e51d33","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:42:16.879Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me set up the cron jobs for the狗仔 agent. I'll create:\n1. A frequent crawling job (every 30 mins during trading hours)\n2. A morning briefing job (9:25 AM)\n3. An afternoon briefing job (13:00)\n\nThese will be isolated agent jobs that use the crawler and then push results to the main agent via message.\n\nActually, looking at the existing setup, the cron jobs are managed by the main agent. For the狗仔 to work as a true separate agent, I would need to configure the openclaw.json with a new agent. But given this is a Miaoda hosted environment, I might not have that level of control.\n\n\nThe most straightforward approach is to set up isolated agent cron jobs that handle the狗仔's core functions—crawling on a schedule, processing the data, and pushing summaries to the main session. I could also make these jobs respond when the user specifically asks for news by creating dedicated cron tasks for periodic crawling and targeted briefings.","thinkingSignature":"51777cb445213dc46571d62f4eb01da9cd6e1646fd89e6df35094c56b58689f7"},{"type":"text","text":"现在创建 cron 任务，让狗仔定时工作：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ft3evisw62p7_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"狗仔·30分钟巡逻","schedule":{"expr":"*/30 7-22 * * 1-5","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"你是狗仔，财经媒体爬虫。\n\n立即执行以下任务：\n1. 运行: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/crawler.py run\n2. 获取最近资讯: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/crawler.py recent --hours=0.5 --limit=15\n3. 获取热门股票: python3 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/crawler.py hot --hours=2\n\n如果发现以下类型的重大资讯（importance=2），立即生成简报：\n- 利好/利空消息\n- 监管政策变化\n- 个股重大公告\n- 板块突发新闻\n\n简报格式：\n【🐕 狗仔快讯】HH:MM\n\n[重要资讯]\n● [标题]\n  来源: [媒体] | 时间: [时间]\n  摘要: [内容]\n\n[热门个股]（最近2小时）\n1. [股票名/代码] -