{"type":"message","id":"c8f777ed","parentId":"36b6dc71","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:46:31.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Need to install the playwright browsers. Let me do that, but it might take a while.Actually, let me think of a simpler approach. The issue is that these sites have anti-scraping measures. Instead of trying to bypass them with a browser, let me try alternative data sources that are more accessible:\n\n1. Use the 同花顺 or 东方财富 APIs which are working\n2. Use 聚合数据/百度股市通 等开放API\n3. Use RSS feeds where available\n4. Try to find other accessible financial news sources\n\nLet me check if there are any RSS feeds available, or if I can use alternative approaches.Actually, let me try to install the playwright browsers since the CLI playwright is already installed on the system.","thinkingSignature":"c3303fcc544862287c38551cfdf4c9943f065f45f38ac986decc437eccd12486"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cau03diz2n2k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai && npx playwright install chromium 2>&1 | tail -10","yieldMs":110000,"timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50463,"output":227,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80571,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774212385154}}
