{"type":"message","id":"67619fbe","parentId":"21cf5513","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:49:40.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The page is loading properly and we can see the content. Now I need to extract the data properly. The issue with my earlier selector was that it was looking for `class*=\"telegraph-item\"` but the actual structure seems different. Let me look at the HTML structure more carefully and extract the articles properly.The body text shows the articles with time stamps. I need to refine the extraction logic. Let me fix the browser_crawler.py to properly extract the articles.","thinkingSignature":"3a2ac1cb6016047846741ab9ef198e9b226ea72ad22a56feee2cf43c449f4deb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4j763e7texh1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai && python3 -c \"\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\nwith sync_playwright() as p:\n    browser = p.chromium.launch(\n        headless=True,\n        args=['--no-sandbox', '--disable-dev-shm-usage', '--disable-gpu']\n    )\n    page = browser.new_page()\n    page.goto('https://www.cls.cn/telegraph', wait_until='networkidle', timeout=20000)\n    page.wait_for_timeout(5000)\n    \n    # 用evaluate直接用JavaScript提取数据\n    articles = page.evaluate('''\n        () => {\n            // 找所有包含时间的文章条目\n            // 财联社页面结构: 左侧列表，每条有时间戳\n            const results = [];\n            const items = document.querySelectorAll('body > div > div > div');\n            \n            // 直接搜索带有财联社电的条目\n            const bodyHTML = document.body.innerHTML;\n            // 用正则提取时间+内容\n            const regex = /(\\\\d{2}:\\\\d{2}:\\\\d{2})\\\\s*([\\\\s\\\\S]*?)(?=\\\\d{2}:\\\\d{2}:\\\\d{2}|$)/g;\n            let match;\n            while ((match = regex.exec(bodyHTML)) !== null && results.length < 20) {\n                const time = match[1];\n                const content = match[2].replace(/<[^>]+>/g, '').trim();\n                if (content.length > 20 && content.includes('财联社')) {\n                    results.push({time, content: content.substring(0, 100)});\n                }\n            }\n            return results.slice(0, 15);\n        }\n    ''')\n    print('财联社找到:', len(articles), '条')\n    for a in articles[:5]:\n        print(f'  {a}')\n    \n    browser.close()\n\" 2>&1","timeout":35}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56547,"output":543,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86971,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774212558020}}
