{"type":"message","id":"c21c1476","parentId":"35221bbc","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:52:36.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I also need to update the code that processes the extracted items. Let me look at the full flow and make sure the items are saved correctly.Actually, the `items` returned from `crawl_taoguba()` is a list of dicts with `title`, `reads`, `time`, but it needs to have `url`, `source`, `summary`, etc. for the `save()` function. Let me check how it's being processed in `run_browser_crawl()` and make sure it works.Actually, looking at the code flow:\n1. `crawl_taoguba()` returns items with `{'title': ..., 'reads': ..., 'time': ...}`2. In `run_browser_crawl()`: `saved = sum(save(item) for item in items)`\n3. `save()` expects keys like: `title, summary, source, url, category, tags, stocks, published_at, importance`\n\nSo the items returned from `crawl_taoguba()` are missing `url`, `source`, `summary`, `category`, `published_at`, `importance`. \n\nThe items only have `title`, `reads`, `time` - I need to add those missing fields before they get passed to `save()`.","thinkingSignature":"1428ce046b8f812774dc2ae5e88e44445e03f2d48b61e435e175ff9452b89b97"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cpqm1vb45ir0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/scripts/browser_crawler.py","offset":170,"limit":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65998,"output":323,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96202,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774212748992}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b80f6b3","parentId":"c21c1476","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:52:36.943Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_cpqm1vb45ir0_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\ndef run_browser_crawl():\n    \"\"\"主函数\"\"\"\n    print(f\"[{datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M:%S')}] 狗仔浏览器巡逻...\")\n    \n    all_new = 0\n    \n    # 财联社\n    try:\n        items = crawl_cailian()\n        saved = sum(save(item) for item in items)\n        print(f\"  财联社: {len(items)}条, 新增{saved}条\")\n        log_crawl('财联社(浏览器)', saved, 'ok')\n        all_new += saved\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  财联社: 失败 {e}\")\n        log_crawl('财联社(浏览器)', 0, 'error', str(e))\n    time.sleep(2)\n    \n    # 淘股吧\n    try:\n        items = crawl_taoguba()\n        saved = sum(save(item) for item in items)\n        print(f\"  淘股吧: {len(items)}条, 新增{saved}条\")\n        log_crawl('淘股吧(浏览器)', saved, 'ok')\n        all_new += saved\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  淘股吧: 失败 {e}\")\n        log_crawl('淘股吧(浏览器)', 0, 'error', str(e))\n    time.sleep(2)\n    \n    # 雪球 - 备用API方式\n    try:\n        items = crawl_xueqiu_fallback()\n        saved = sum(save(item) for item in items)\n        print(f\"  雪球: {len(items)}条, 新增{saved}条\")\n        log_crawl('雪球(API)', saved, 'ok')\n        all_new += saved\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  雪球: 失败 {e}\")\n        log_crawl('雪球(API)', 0, 'error', str(e))\n    \n    print(f\"  共新增 {all_new} 条资讯\")\n    return all_new\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    run_browser_crawl()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774212756929}}
