{"type":"message","id":"4a9197ba","parentId":"c61b36cb","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:53:56.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give a summary of what's done. The 狗仔 system is up and running. Let me provide a clear summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"095c4eda6ce75dc5facc6edcefc0b92b43b1461b885befb83366aa8a4aba35e5"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定！狗仔现在全速运转 🐕\n\n**当前进度：**\n\n| 信源 | 状态 | 方法 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 财联社 | ✅ 正常 | 浏览器渲染 |\n| 淘股吧 | ✅ 正常 | 浏览器渲染 |\n| 东方财富 | ✅ 正常 | HTTP API |\n| 同花顺 | ✅ 正常 | HTTP API |\n| 雪球 | ⚠️ 有WAF | 待解决 |\n\n**数据库：79 条资讯**（还在持续增加）\n\n**雪球的问题：** 它用阿里云WAF做了IP检测，浏览器会自动过验证但程序直接访问会被拦。解决方案：\n1. 换个出口IP（代理池）\n2. 用selenium过验证（慢）\n3. 放弃雪球，用其他社区替代（e.g. 摩尔金融、证券之星）\n\n要不要继续搞雪球，还是先这样跑着看？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":73678,"output":226,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103785,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774212830118}}
