{"type":"message","id":"419a1ca2","parentId":"37985ca9","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:52:00.040Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-23 05:51:38 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0 [msg:om_x100b53320855d8a0b24042ef19f7eca]\nSystem: [2026-03-23 05:51:59 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0 [msg:om_x100b5332093d40a0b3b78ac7227d6e3]\n\nNote: The previous agent run was aborted by the user. Resume carefully or ask for clarification.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5332093d40a0b3b78ac7227d6e3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-23 05:51 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\"\n}\n```\n\n你看下这个对接文档https://stock.quicktiny.cn/developer"}],"timestamp":1774216320030}}
{"type":"message","id":"b6be2e55","parentId":"419a1ca2","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:52:03.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to look at a developer documentation page at https://stock.quicktiny.cn/developer. Let me fetch this URL to see what it contains.","thinkingSignature":"e21123fbe8f37ffd61b85449490f576c81bc19e03773e3caa19af382774dcf94"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bs3ppo6v04fh_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-fetch/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":79,"cacheRead":107751,"cacheWrite":299,"totalTokens":108257,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774216320036}}
{"type":"message","id":"3089059b","parentId":"b6be2e55","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:52:03.687Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bs3ppo6v04fh_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-fetch\r\ndescription: \"Use when user needs to crawl or fetch a specific URL to extract/summarize its content. Provides necessary command usage instructions for fetching known URLs. 触发词：网页抓取, 抓取网页, 提取网页内容, web crawl, 爬取, fetch url, 总结网页, 抓取 URL, 读取网页\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_fetch\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Fetch\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` 抓取指定网页内容，由 AI 自动总结/提取。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--url` | 网页 URL | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary（见 miaoda-web-search skill）\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL（见 miaoda-web-search skill）→ web-crawl 提取详情\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 抓取指定 URL 并提取信息\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url https://example.com/pricing\r\n\r\n# 搜索 → 深入抓取：先搜索找到目标 URL，再抓取提取详细信息\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url <搜索结果中的URL>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`（见 miaoda-web-search skill） |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774216323647}}
{"type":"message","id":"97c655df","parentId":"3089059b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T21:52:06.073Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me use the web fetch skill to get the content of this URL.","thinkingSignature":"8146fc08062c620a83725ca2e6f7e1e68cb59a927e024548f7c82069c0884059"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t59bukus4vbb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url https://stock.quicktiny.cn/developer 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78854,"output":73,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108808,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774216323680}}
