{"type":"message","id":"b288ac6b","parentId":"0725a827","timestamp":"2026-03-22T22:08:24.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both /developer/my-key and /developer/apikey redirect to login. This means the session wasn't maintained. Let me try a different approach - use a single browser context with cookies and try the API page again.\n\nActually, looking at the API docs, I have enough information to understand the API structure. The key endpoints are:\n- `/search` - 股票搜索\n- `/kline/:code` - K线数据\n- `/minute/:code` - 分时数据\n- `/rank` - 股票排行\n- `/market-overview` - 市场概况\n- `/trading-calendar` - 交易日历\n- `/ladder` - 涨停梯队\n\n\n- `/limit-up/filter` - 涨停筛选\n- `/limit-up/premium` - 涨停溢价\n- `/anomalies` - 异动检测\n- `/capital-flow` - 资金流向\n- `/sector-analysis` - 板块分析\n- `/correlation/:code` - 股票关联\n- `/concepts/ranking` - 概念排行\n- `/concepts/:tsCode/stocks` - 概念成分股\n- `/hotlist` - 智能热榜\n- `/research-reports` - 研报数据\n- `/auction` - 竞价数据\n- `/briefings` - 每日简报\n- `/dragon-tiger` - 龙虎榜\n\nThe authentication requires a Bearer token in the Authorization header with the format `lb_your_key_here`, and the base URL is `https://stock.quicktiny.cn/api/openclaw`. The user's account doesn't seem to have an API key generated yet, but they mentioned something about integrating with OpenClaw skills - I should ask them about that.\n\nActually, looking back at what they said about \"openclaw skills already online\" - this might be a platform that has OpenClaw skills already integrated. Let me search for the OpenClaw skill on ClawHub to see what's available for this platform.","thinkingSignature":"12db32df42ac6b372b5014277723f3383d9e37240527fee3d49b8ae609f57a82"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xdd3mh7k82tr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search \"quicktiny\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"clawhub not found\"\nnpm list -g clawhub 2>/dev/null || echo \"clawhub not installed globally\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"min