{"type":"message","id":"8330beb3","parentId":"3dd5d428","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:05:09.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full database structure. Let me present it clearly.","thinkingSignature":"d19d4af288e0cd4adbea76c2d0a1c0d370bc8f728b6a788791f1f84813fa356d"},{"type":"text","text":"**A股数据库结构**（`astock.db`）\n\n| 表名 | 记录数 | 用途 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| `predictions` | 27 | 每日预测结果 |\n| `daily_stats` | 0 | 每日市场情绪统计 |\n| `calibration` | 0 | 概率标定（预测准确率） |\n| `coef_log` | 0 | 系数调整日志 |\n| `positions` | 0 | 持仓记录 |\n| `historical_zt` | 0 | 历史涨停股 |\n\n**predictions 表核心字段：**\n- `date/code/name` - 日期、股票代码、名称\n- `lb` - 连板数\n- `jb_prob/dz_prob` - 晋级概率、跌振概率\n- `dist_N/N1/N2` - 晋级概率分布\n- `outcome/detail/actual_boards` - T+1实际结局\n\n**K线数据**不在这，在 parquet 文件里：\n```\n/data/astock/kline/batches/batch_001~020.parquet\n  → date, code, open, high, low, close, volume, amount\n  → 3800只股票，197.9万行\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97350,"output":278,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127509,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774220702053}}
{"type":"message","id":"86ab1d15","parentId":"8330beb3","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:06:12.906Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-23 07:06:12 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0 [msg:om_x100b533310f068a0c4958b60f8cbe91]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b533310f068a0c4958b60f8cbe91\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-23 07:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\"\n}\n```\n\n你不存数据库是有什么考虑吗"}],"timestamp":1774220772894}}
{"type":"message","id":"7af35070","parentId":"86ab1d15","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:06:30.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why I don't store the data in a database, and what considerations there are. Let me think about this:\n\n1. The K-line data is stored in parquet files, not in SQLite\n2. The predictions/positions are in SQLite\n3. The user might be asking why I store K-line data in parquet files instead of importing everything into SQLite\n\nLet me think about the considerations:\n\n**For K-line data in parquet:**\n- Each stock has ~550 trading days of data\n- 3800 stocks × 550 = ~2 million rows\n- SQLite with millions of rows gets slow for analytical queries\n- Parquet is columnar, compresses well, and is fast for range queries on time-series data\n\n\n- Parquet files are already partitioned by batch, so I could further partition by month or year to optimize queries\n\n**For reference data in SQLite:**\n- Predictions, positions, calibration results—relational data that needs ACID transactions and random access updates\n- Schema is well-defined and relatively stable\n\nSo the real question is whether I should migrate everything into SQLite. With millions of rows of K-line data, that would be slow for analytical queries, and the data is already processed by BaoStock in batch format. The separation actually makes sense, though there are tradeoffs to consider if the user wants a single source of truth.","thinkingSignature":"73bc3f8801a0c92921b47f857f2af3bbeeb9f73b1769c2b44058ee347aa65cb5"},{"type":"text","text":"两个原因：\n\n**1. 数据量**\n- K线：3800只 × 550天 ≈ 200万行 → parquet 压缩后 ~70MB，SQLite 存这个量级会很慢\n- parquet 是列式存储，按时间范围查询比 SQLite 快一个量级\n\n**2. 使用模式**\n- K线是**append-only**的历史数据，只读不修改 → 文件存储最省事\n- 预测结果、持仓、系数是**经常更新**的关系数据 → SQLite 更适合\n\n**实际可以考虑的方案：**\n\n| 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 现状（parquet + SQLite） | 各司其职，查询快 | 两套存储 |\n| 全部入 SQLite | 统一管理 | 200万行后变慢 |\n| 全部入 parquet | 查询快 | 修改麻烦，需全量重写 |\n\n现在 parquet 是 append 写入，如果想全部统一到 SQLite 也可以迁，但迁完查询会变慢。你想怎么搞？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":495,"cacheRead":125624,"cacheWrite":1922,"totalTokens":128169,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774220772900}}
