{"type":"message","id":"5c06ffa8","parentId":"ee9b59c6","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:08:23.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the conditions are met to do historical backtesting of the auction strategy and prediction strategy. Let me check:\n\n1. K-line data: We have 3800 stocks, 197.9万 rows, from 2024-01-02 to 2026-03-20 - about 2+ years of data. This is enough for backtesting.\n\n2. The prediction system uses:\n   - auction.py for auction conditions\n   - predict.py for prediction/probability calculation\n   - The system needs historical 涨停 (limit up) data to calculate upgrade probabilities\n\n3. What we still lack:\n   - `historical_zt` table is empty - we don't have historical limit-up stocks stored\n   - `daily_stats` table is empty - no market sentiment data\n   - `calibration` table is empty - no accuracy tracking\n\nSo the main issue is:\n- K-line data: ✅ OK\n- Historical limit-up stocks (涨停股): ❌ Not stored, need to populate from the K-line data\n- The system can identify limit-ups from K-line data (backfill_from_kline.py does this)\n\nThe backfill_from_kline.py script is designed to compute historical 涨停/炸板 from K-line data and save to historical_zt table. We should run that to populate historical_zt, then we can do proper backtesting.\n\nLet me give a clear assessment.","thinkingSignature":"0840e683621d29189414a850906c668ed438120d8eb426236d0d2e8a924430be"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4940f13d81aa_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport pandas as pd, os\nbatch_dir = '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/kline/batches'\nfiles = sorted([f for f in os.listdir(batch_dir) if f.endswith('.parquet')])\n\n# 合并看日期范围\nall_dates = set()\nfor f in files:\n    df = pd.read_parquet(os.path.join(batch_dir, f), columns=['date'])\n    all_dates.update(df['date'].unique())\n\ndates = sorted(all_dates)\nprint(f'K线数据: {len(dates)} 个交易日')\nprint(f'起始: {dates[0]}')\nprint(f'结束: {dates[-1]}')\nprint(f'覆盖: 2024-01-02 ~ 2026-03-20')\n\n# 统计每只股票的日期数\nimport sqlite3\nconn = sqlite3.connect('/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/model/astock.db')\npred = conn.execute('SELECT COUNT(*) FROM predictions').fetchone()[0]\nhist_zt = conn.execute('SELECT COUNT(*) FROM historical_zt').fetchone()[0]\nprint(f'预测记录: {pred} 条')\nprint(f'历史涨停: {hist_zt} 条')\nconn.close()\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":583,"cacheRead":127386,"cacheWrite":678,"totalTokens":128775,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774220885987}}
