{"type":"message","id":"ab0519e9","parentId":"0fbd9492","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:08:35.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So we have:\n- K-line data: 534 trading days, 2024-01-02 to 2026-03-20 ✅\n- Predictions: 27 records ✅  \n- Historical 涨停 (limit-up stocks): 0 records ❌ - this is needed for backtesting\n\nThe historical_zt table is empty because we haven't run the backfill_from_kline.py script to extract limit-up stocks from the K-line data.\n\nThe key question is: can we do backtesting with what we have?\n\nThe backfill_from_kline.py script can:\n1. Read K-line data\n\n\n2. Identify which stocks hit limit-up on each day\n3. Save to historical_zt table\n\nOnce we populate historical_zt, we'd have:\n- Daily limit-up stocks for 534 trading days\n- Auction conditions for each stock\n- Prediction probabilities\n\nThen we can run backtesting by simulating what the prediction system would have done historically. I should tell the user what's missing and what we need to do to enable backtesting.","thinkingSignature":"12537a3639a45fece54339c4819a6d4ac3333ffb49095ada121fa0ac46e8f54d"},{"type":"text","text":"**不满足，还差关键一步：**\n\n| 条件 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| K线数据 | ✅ | 534个交易日，2024-01-02~2026-03-20 |\n| 预测记录 | ✅ | 27条（近期复盘） |\n| 历史涨停股 | ❌ | **0条，空的** |\n| 每日市场情绪 | ❌ | 0条 |\n| 概率标定 | ❌ | 0条 |\n\n**缺的东西：**\n\n`historical_zt`（历史涨停股）是核心——没有它就无法回测\"昨天涨停的股票今天是否晋级\"。\n\n**可以补：**\n用已有的K线数据跑一遍 `backfill_from_kline.py`，从K线里计算出每天哪些股票涨停，写入 `historical_zt` 表。534个交易日 × 每天几十只涨停股，大概能生成 **1-2万条**历史涨停记录。\n\n要跑吗？大概几分钟能跑完。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98969,"output":428,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129278,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774220904142}}
