{"type":"message","id":"bda62e83","parentId":"00fd995b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:14:33.041Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i28eeu8ii9ry_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[07:14:11] 加载K线数据...\nK线加载完成: 3798只股票\n待回测: 26308 条涨停记录\n  进度: 2000/26308\n  进度: 4000/26308\n  进度: 6000/26308\n  进度: 8000/26308\n  进度: 10000/26308\n  进度: 12000/26308\n  进度: 14000/26308\n  进度: 16000/26308\n  进度: 18000/26308\n  进度: 20000/26308\n  进度: 22000/26308\n  进度: 24000/26308\n  进度: 26000/26308\n[07:14:31] 写入预测结果...\n完成! 总预测: 26308 条, 有结局: 26308 条\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"clear-wharf","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[07:14:11] 加载K线数据...\nK线加载完成: 3798只股票\n待回测: 26308 条涨停记录\n  进度: 2000/26308\n  进度: 4000/26308\n  进度: 6000/26308\n  进度: 8000/26308\n  进度: 10000/26308\n  进度: 12000/26308\n  进度: 14000/26308\n  进度: 16000/26308\n  进度: 18000/26308\n  进度: 20000/26308\n  进度: 22000/26308\n  进度: 24000/26308\n  进度: 26000/26308\n[07:14:31] 写入预测结果...\n完成! 总预测: 26308 条, 有结局: 26308 条\n","name":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774221273006}}
{"type":"message","id":"501b369f","parentId":"bda62e83","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:14:49.679Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! All 26,308 historical limit-up stocks now have predictions and outcomes. Now let's run the calibration to build the probability calibration table, and then show the user the results.","thinkingSignature":"7b8228740f35283a7e303313441cc356de95cfbc10679b8cee6e7cc510da9f74"},{"type":"text","text":"写入完成！跑一下概率标定：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6030jduh5t3x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport sqlite3\nfrom collections import defaultdict\n\nDB_PATH = '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/model/astock.db'\nconn = sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\n\n# 读取所有预测\nrows = conn.execute(\"\"\"\n    SELECT jb_prob, lb, outcome FROM predictions \n    WHERE outcome IS NOT NULL AND jb_prob IS NOT NULL\n\"\"\").fetchall()\n\nprint(f\"总样本: {len(rows)} 条\")\n\n# 按晋级概率分段统计\nbuckets = defaultdict(lambda: {'total': 0, 'actual_jb': 0, 'pred_sum': 0})\n\nfor jb_prob, lb, outcome in rows:\n    bucket = int(jb_prob // 5)  # 按5%分桶\n    buckets[bucket]['total'] += 1\n    buckets[bucket]['pred_sum'] += jb_prob\n    if outcome == '晋级':\n        buckets[bucket]['actual_jb'] += 1\n\n# 写入calibration表\nconn.execute(\"DELETE FROM calibration\")\n\nprint(\"\\n概率标定结果:\")\nprint(f\"{'桶区间':<12} {'预测均值':<10} {'实际晋级率':<12} {'样本数':<8} {'偏差':<10}\")\nprint(\"-\" * 55)\n\nfor bucket in sorted(buckets.keys()):\n    data = buckets[bucket]\n    if data['total'] < 10:\n        continue\n    \n    pred_avg = data['pred_sum'] / data['total']\n    actual_rate = data['actual_jb'] / data['total'] * 100\n    bias = actual_rate - pred_avg\n    low = bucket * 5\n    high = (bucket + 1) * 5\n    \n    conn.execute(\"\"\"\n        INSERT INTO calibration (bucket, total_sample_count, total_predicted_prob_sum, total_actual_jb_sum)\n        VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)\n    \"\"\", (bucket, data['total'], data['pred_sum'], data['actual_jb']))\n    \n    bias_str = f\"{bias:+.1f}%\" if abs(bias) < 50 else \"N/A\"\n    print(f\"{low:>3}-{high:<3}%     {pred_avg:>6.1f}%    {actual_rate:>8.1f}%    {data['total']:<8} {bias_str:>10}\")\n\nconn.commit()\n\n# 总体统计\ntotal = sum(d['total'] for d in buckets.values())\nactual_total = sum(d['actual_jb'] for d in buckets.values())\npred_total = sum(d['pred_sum'] for d in buckets.values())\nprint(f\"\\n总体准确率: {actual_total}/{total} = {actual_total/total*100:.1f}%\")\nprint(f\"总体预测均值: {pred_total/total:.1f}%\")\n\n# 晋级/断板/续涨分布\noutcomes = defaultdict(int)\nfor _, _, outcome in rows:\n    outcomes[outcome] += 1\n\nprint(f\"\\n结局分布:\")\nfor k, v in sorted(outcomes.items(), key=lambda x: -x[1]):\n    print(f\"  {k}: {v} ({v/len(rows)*100:.1f}%)\")\n\nconn.close()\nEOF\n","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":111456,"output":783,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142120,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774221273039}}
