{"type":"message","id":"5bdfd83a","parentId":"57e42783","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:15:58.620Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hq5ivmsucuuq_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"加载K线...\nK线: 3798只股票\n补全 26308 条预测...\n  进度 5000/26308\n  进度 10000/26308\n  进度 15000/26308\n  进度 20000/26308\n  进度 25000/26308\n补全完成!\n\n概率标定:\n桶        预测均值       实际率        样本       偏差\n---------------------------------------------\n  0-5  %      4.1%     19.4%  5219     +15.3%\n  5-10 %      7.2%     19.9%  14125    +12.7%\n 10-15 %     12.3%     25.7%  4426     +13.4%\n 15-20 %     17.5%     39.1%  1928     +21.6%\n 20-25 %     22.6%     33.8%  355      +11.2%\n 25-30 %     27.2%     34.3%  143      +7.1%\n 30-35 %     32.4%     38.1%  84       +5.7%\n 35-40 %     37.9%     57.1%  21       +19.2%\n\n总体: 5926/26308 = 22.5%\n\n结局分布:\n  续涨: 16239 (61.7%)\n  晋级: 5926 (22.5%)\n  断板: 4063 (15.4%)\n  停牌: 80 (0.3%)\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"rapid-zephyr","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"加载K线...\nK线: 3798只股票\n补全 26308 条预测...\n  进度 5000/26308\n  进度 10000/26308\n  进度 15000/26308\n  进度 20000/26308\n  进度 25000/26308\n补全完成!\n\n概率标定:\n桶        预测均值       实际率        样本       偏差\n---------------------------------------------\n  0-5  %      4.1%     19.4%  5219     +15.3%\n  5-10 %      7.2%     19.9%  14125    +12.7%\n 10-15 %     12.3%     25.7%  4426     +13.4%\n 15-20 %     17.5%     39.1%  1928     +21.6%\n 20-25 %     22.6%     33.8%  355      +11.2%\n 25-30 %     27.2%     34.3%  143      +7.1%\n 30-35 %     32.4%     38.1%  84       +5.7%\n 35-40 %     37.9%     57.1%  21       +19.2%\n\n总体: 5926/26308 = 22.5%\n\n结局分布:\n  续涨: 16239 (61.7%)\n  晋级: 5926 (22.5%)\n  断板: 4063 (15.4%)\n  停牌: 80 (0.3%)\n","name":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774221358583}}
{"type":"message","id":"078cd6d5","parentId":"5bdfd83a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:16:12.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great results! The backtest is complete. Now let me present the results to the user.\n\nKey findings:\n1. Total samples: 26,308 historical limit-up stocks\n2. Overall actual promotion rate: 22.5% (5,926 out of 26,308)\n\nProbability calibration:\n- Low probability buckets (0-5%, 5-10%, 10-15%) consistently underpredict actual rates by +12-15%\n- The model's predictions are systematically lower than actual outcomes\n- This means the BASE_PROBS might be too conservative\n\nOutcome distribution:\n- 续涨 (continued rise): 61.7%\n\n\n- 晋级 (promoted): 22.5%\n- 断板 (broken): 15.4%\n- 停牌 (suspended): 0.3%\n\nThe analysis reveals clear inefficiencies in the current probability estimates—the model systematically underestimates晋级 likelihood across all buckets, so recalibrating BASE_PROBS upward would improve prediction accuracy. I should present these findings to the user.","thinkingSignature":"33f9f8fdf5cc072cdb26e2a0e26835081ef3e19fd233066c0243af553a77c5e9"},{"type":"text","text":"回测完成！数据非常有料 🐕\n\n**历史回测结果：26,308 条涨停记录**\n\n**结局分布：**\n| 结局 | 数量 | 占比 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 续涨（炸板） | 16,239 | 61.7% |\n| 晋级（继续涨停） | 5,926 | **22.5%** |\n| 断板（跌停） | 4,063 | 15.4% |\n\n**概率标定（预测 vs 实际）：**\n\n| 预测区间 | 预测均值 | 实际晋级率 | 偏差 | 样本 |\n|----------|----------|------------|------|------|\n| 0-5% | 4.1% | 19.4% | **+15.3%** | 5,219 |\n| 5-10% | 7.2% | 19.9% | **+12.7%** | 14,125 |\n| 10-15% | 12.3% | 25.7% | **+13.4%** | 4,426 |\n| 15-20% | 17.5% | 39.1% | **+21.6%** | 1,928 |\n| 20-25% | 22.6% | 33.8% | **+11.2%** | 355 |\n\n**结论：预测系统性地低估了晋级概率！** 实际晋级率远高于预测值，说明 `BASE_PROBS` 需要上调。22.5% 的总体晋级率意味着：**首板次日继续涨停的概率接近 1/4**，远超大多数\"低板位\"预测的 10-15%。\n\n需要我根据这个校准数据调整预测系数吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":115549,"output":600,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":146030,"co