{"type":"message","id":"3138288d","parentId":"70f43e5a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:19:37.038Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to adjust the calibration coefficients based on the backtest results and then predict today's晋级概率 for the stocks that are predicted to be in the auction pattern.\n\nLooking at the backtest results, the actual晋级 rate is systematically higher than predicted. The bias is:\n- 0-5%: +15.3% (predicted 4.1%, actual 19.4%)\n- 5-10%: +12.7% (predicted 7.2%, actual 19.9%)\n- 10-15%: +13.4% (predicted 12.3%, actual 25.7%)\n\n\n- 15-20%: +21.6% (predicted 17.5%, actual 39.1%)\n- 20-25%: +11.2% (predicted 22.6%, actual 33.8%)\n\nThe pattern is clear—my predictions are consistently underestimating by 10-20 percentage points. I need to apply a correction factor to realign the predicted probabilities with actual outcomes.\n\nLooking at the actual晋级 rates across different prediction ranges, they're clustering around 20-40% when I'd expect them to fall in the 4-37% range. The most efficient approach is to increase BASE_PROBS directly rather than tweaking individual coefficients. I'll recalculate the晋级 probabilities using the empirically observed rates and rerun the predictions to see if they match today's auction candidates.","thinkingSignature":"8ad83ddfc40b5e97fe4c8f899dd7a65fc82a4fcca741d58113c5119bb3acb80d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fz8gc7lgn5ht_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock && python3 << 'EOF'\n\"\"\"\n根据历史回测校准结果调整预测概率，然后预测今日竞价个股\n\"\"\"\nimport sys, os\nsys.path.insert(0, '.')\nimport sqlite3\nimport pandas as pd\nimport akshare as ak\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nBATCH_DIR = '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/kline/batches'\nDB_PATH = '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/model/astock.db'\n\n# 加载K线\nfiles = sorted([f for f in os.listdir(BATCH_DIR) if f.endswith('.parquet')])\nall_dfs = [pd.read_parquet(os.path.join(BATCH_DIR, f)) for f in files]\nkline = pd.concat(all_dfs, ignore_index=True).dropna(subset=['date', 'code', 'close', 'high', 'open', 'volume'])\n\nkline_dict = {}\nfor code, grp in kline.groupby('code'):\n    grp_sorted = grp.sort_values('date')\n    kline_dict[code] = {'dates': list(grp_sorted['date']), 'data': grp_sorted.set_index('date').to_dict('index')}\n\n# 校准系数（基于回测实际晋级率）\n# 实际晋级率 ≈ 预测晋级的20-40%，说明原系数偏低约2-3倍\n# 校准策略：直接用实际晋级率作为参考，调整BASE_PROBS\nCALIBRATION = {\n    1: 0.20,   # 首板实际晋级率 ~20%\n    2: 0.28,   # 2板实际晋级率 ~28%\n    3: 0.35,   # 3板实际晋级率 ~35%\n    4: 0.25,   # 4板+实际晋级率 ~25%\n    5: 0.15,   # 5板+实际晋级率 ~15%\n}\n\nprint(f\"[{datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M:%S')}] 获取今日涨停数据...\")\n\n# 获取昨日（最近交易日）涨停池\ntry:\n    yesterday = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=1)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\n    zt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date=yesterday)\n    print(f\"昨日涨停: {len(zt_df)}只\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"获取失败: {e}\")\n    exit(1)\n\n# 获取板块统计\nsector_raw = {}\nfor _, r in zt_df.iterrows():\n    ind = str(r.get('行业', '其他'))\n    if ind not in sector_raw:\n        sector_raw[ind] = {'total': 0, 'codes': []}\n    sector_raw[ind]['total'] += 1\n    sector_raw[ind]['codes'].append(str(r['代码']).zfill(6))\n\nprint(f\"\\n板块效应（>=3只联动）:\")\nhot_sectors = {k: v for k, v in sector_raw.items() if v['total'] >= 3}\nfor ind, data in sorted(hot_sectors.items(), key=lambda x: -x[1]['total'])[:5]:\n    print(f\"  🚀 {ind}: {data['total']}只\")\n\n# 预测每只涨停股\nprint(f\"\\n{'='*70}\")\nprint(f\"  {'代码':<8} {'名称':<10} {'板':<4} {'校准后晋级%':<12} {'原晋级%':<10} {'校准幅度'}\")\nprint(f\"{'='*70}\")\n\nresults = []\nfrom predict import calc_adj\n\nfor _, row in zt_df.iterrows():\n    code = str(row['代码']).zfill(6)\n    name = str(row.get('名称', code))\n    lb = int(row.get('连板数', 1) or 1)\n    industry = str(row.get('行业', '其他'))\n    \n    kl = kline_dict.get(code, {}).get('data', {}).get(yesterday.replace('-',''))\n    if not kl:\n        # 用最近日期\n        dates = kline_dict.get(code, {}).get('dates', [])\n        if dates:\n            kl = kline_dict[code]['data'].get(dates[-1])\n    \n    if not kl:\n        continue\n    \n    # 计算校准后晋级概率\n    base_prob = CALIBRATION.get(min(lb+1, 5), 0.15)\n    \n    # 计算调整因子（沿用原有逻辑）\n    vr = kl.get('vr', 1)\n    rsi = kl.get('rsi', 50)\n    trend = kl.get('trend', '震荡')\n    \n    adj = 1.0\n    if trend == '上升通道':\n        adj *= 1.2\n    elif trend == '下降通道':\n        adj *= 0.7\n    if rsi < 40:\n        adj *= 1.15\n    elif rsi > 70:\n        adj *= 0.85\n    if 0.5 <= vr < 1.0:\n        adj *= 1.1\n    elif vr >= 1.5:\n        adj *= 0.9\n    \n    # 板块效应\n    if sector_raw.get(industry, {}).get('total', 0) >= 3:\n        adj *= 1.15\n    \n    jb_prob_cal = min(base_prob * adj, 0.70) * 100\n    \n    # 原晋级概率（从数据库）\n    results.append({\n        'code': code, 'name': name, 'lb': lb, 'industry': industry,\n        'jb_prob_cal': jb_prob_cal,\n        'base_prob': base_prob * 100,\n        'adj': adj,\n        'vr': vr, 'rsi': rsi, 'trend': trend,\n    })\n\n# 按校准后晋级概率排序\nresults.sort(key=lambda x: -x['jb_prob_cal'])\n\n# 晋级分布\ngt30 = sum(1 for r in results if r['jb_prob_cal'] > 30)\ngt15 = sum(1 for r in results if 15 < r['jb_prob_cal'] <= 30)\nlt15 = len(results) - gt30 - gt15\n\nprint(f\"\\n晋级分布：>30%: {gt30}只 / 15-30%: {gt15}只 / <15%: {lt15}只\")\nprint(f\"\\n{'='*70}\")\nprint(f\"【重点竞价】（晋级概率>20%）\")\nprint(f\"{'='*70}\")\nprint(f\"{'代码':<8} {'名称':<10} {'板':<4} {'晋级%':<10} {'竞价区间':<14} {'量比':<6} {'板块'}\")\nprint(f\"{'-'*70}\")\n\nfor r in results:\n    if r['jb_prob_cal'] <= 20:\n        break\n    lb = r['lb']\n    adj = r['adj']\n    \n    # 竞价区间计算\n    if lb >= 3:\n        ok_range = \"1~6%\"\n    elif sector_raw.get(r['industry'], {}).get('total', 0) >= 3:\n        ok_range = \"3~8%\"\n    elif r['jb_prob_cal'] > 20:\n        ok_range = \"3~7%\"\n    else:\n        ok_range = \"4~7%\"\n    \n    print(f\"{r['code']:<8} {r['name']:<10} {lb}板   {r['jb_prob_cal']:>5.1f}%   {ok_range:<14} {r['vr']:>4.1f}  {r['industry'][:6]}\")\n\nprint(f\"\\n{'='*70}\")\nprint(f\"【次级关注】（晋级概率15-20%）\")\nprint(f\"{'-'*70}\")\nfor r in results:\n    if r['jb_prob_cal'] <= 15:\n        break\n    if r['jb_prob_cal'] <= 20:\n        print(f\"{r['code']:<8} {r['name']:<10} {r['lb']}板   {r['jb_prob_cal']:>5.1f}%   {r['industry'][:10]}\")\n\nprint(f\"\\n总预测: {len(results)}只涨停股\")\nprint(f\"校准参考: 历史实际晋级率 22.5%，原预测系统性低估10-20%\")\n\nEOF\n","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":2138,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":120283,"totalTokens":152430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774221532062}}
