{"type":"compaction","id":"660bdd4f","parentId":"3f2ab4d7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:21:35.400Z","summary":"## Goal\nBuild an A股 trading intelligence system with: (1) daily review + auction prediction, (2) financial news monitoring via a dedicated \"狗仔\" agent, (3) background K-line data fetching from BaoStock, (4) **new: integrate with 連板天梯 platform** (quicktiny.cn) via its developer API.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Data fetching must auto-retry up to 3 times on interruption\n- Cron jobs should run during trading hours (Mon–Fri, 7–22 Shanghai time)\n- News crawling should prioritize: 财联社, 淘股吧, 东方财富, 同花顺; 雪球 has WAF protection and is optional\n- All Feishu reports sent to user `ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0`\n- **quicktiny.cn integration**: credentials must be sent via DM only (not in group); use and discard, do not persist\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Created cron \"A股竞价模式筛选\" — trading days 08:25:30 Asia/Shanghai, uses BaoStock + auction_ok logic\n- [x] Created cron \"狗仔·30分钟巡逻\" — every 30 min 7–22 Mon–Fri\n- [x] Created cron \"狗仔·盘前简报\" — 09:25 Mon–Fri\n- [x] Created workspace `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/` with SOUL.md, AGENTS.md\n- [x] Created `scripts/crawler.py` (HTTP API — 东方财富 + 同花顺 working)\n- [x] Created `scripts/browser_crawler.py` (playwright — 财联社 + 淘股吧 working)\n- [x] Installed playwright + chromium for browser rendering\n- [x] Database `data/news.db` has 79+ news records from 4 sources\n- [x] Background K-line fetch **completed** (PID 301484, exit code 0) — full 9599 stocks processed\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] **quicktiny.cn API integration**: awaiting user DM with login credentials to access developer documentation\n\n### Blocked\n- [ ] 雪球 (xueqiu.com) — aliyun WAF anti-bot protection blocks all access attempts (API + browser both fail)\n- [ ] 雪球 access remains unresolved\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Separate HTTP + browser crawlers**: Keep crawler.py (HTTP, fast) + browser_crawler.py (playwright, for JS-rendered sites)\n- **No 雪球 for now**: WAF too aggressive; skip until proxy or alternative found\n- **狗仔 as sub-agent**: Not a full OpenClaw agent — runs as isolated cron sessions with SOUL.md personality\n- **quicktiny.cn via DM credentials**: User will send login info via private DM; will log in via playwright and scrape API docs, then discard credentials\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Receive user's DM with quicktiny.cn credentials → log in via playwright → navigate to developer page → extract API documentation\n2. Analyze API endpoints, auth method, data format from the docs\n3. Determine if BaoStock data can be supplemented or replaced by quicktiny.cn API\n4. Backfill historical_zt and daily_stats tables once K-line data is fully processed\n\n## Critical Context\n```\nData dir:         /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/kline/\nAstock WS:        /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/\nGouzai WS:        /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/\nGouzai data:      /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/gouzai/data/news.db\nStock list:       /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/stock_list.json\nDB (astock):      /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock/stock.db\n  - predictions:  27 rows (date=20260320)\n  - positions: 0, daily_stats: 0, historical_zt: 0\nQuicktiny WS:     quicktiny.cn (連板天梯 platform)\nQuicktiny URL:    https://stock.quicktiny.cn/developer\n  - Status: requires login; \"openclaw skills已上线\"\n  - Features: 行情信息, 连板天梯, 共识复盘, 自选股, 涨停基因,\n    题材库, 板块轮动, 涨停筛选, 龙虎榜, 异动中心, 量化实验室,\n    热点资讯, 个股分析, 多股对比 etc.\n  - Auth required: email/password\n  - Awaiting: credentials via DM\n```\n\n## Decisions\n- **Quicktiny integration via playwright**: Page is SPA/Vue.js; `document.body.innerText` via `page.evaluate()` is the correct method (not `page.inner_text` which caused `TypeError: page.inner_text is not a function`)\n- **Multi-route exploration**: Tried `/developer`, `/developer/docs`, `/docs`, `/api`, `/developer/api`, `/skills`, `/login`, `/register` — all require auth or return 404\n- **Credential handling**: Must be DM-only; do not persist after use\n\n## Open TODOs\n- [ ] Receive quicktiny.cn credentials via DM\n- [ ] Log in and scrape developer docs from https://stock.quicktiny.cn/developer\n- [ ] Identify API endpoints, auth scheme, data format for 連板天梯\n- [ ] Resolve 雪球 WAF (proxy or alternative source)\n- [ ] Backfill historical_zt and daily_stats tables once K-line fetch complete\n- [ ] Verify 狗仔 cron tasks fire correctly starting 07:00\n- [ ] First 狗仔 盘前简报 at 09:25 (2026-03-23)\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- BaoStock free tier rate-limited; fetch sleeps 20–70ms between requests\n- Browser-based crawling uses headless chromium via playwright; `page.inner_text` is not a valid API (use `page.evaluate(() => document.body.innerText)`)\n- All cron jobs deliver to Feishu `ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0`\n- quicktiny.cn credentials must be DM-only; use and discard\n\n## Pending user asks\n- **User offered quicktiny.cn credentials via DM** — awaiting receipt. User said \"给你用户名和密码行吗\" and was instructed to send via DM.\n\n## Exact identifiers\n```\nCron job IDs:\n  狗仔·30分钟巡逻:      d8ad4227-fff2-48da-b09a-a13c9ec4f272\n  A股竞价模式筛选:       dc676ffd-0c3d-470b-9a6d-93e3c01dfcc8\n  A股每日竞价复盘:       03ab253b-2906-4537-bb8a-50d79929a2e1\n  狗仔·盘前简报:        05380b09-413d-4018-80bd-983d42984d3d\n\nSession key (main):     agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\nUser Feishu ID:         ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\n\nMessage IDs (recent):\n  om_x100b53323bca70a8b220a4f331d50f8  (user: 给你用户名和密码行吗)\n  om_x100b53320b19cca8b22fdf287c3b0f3  (user: 看下这个对接文档)\n\nBackground fetch PID:   301484 (COMPLETED, code 0, 2026-03-23 05:38:49)\nA-stock total:          9599 支A股 (fully processed)\n\nQuicktiny platform:\n  URL:        https://stock.quicktiny.cn/developer\n  Skills URL: https://stock.quicktiny.cn/skills\n  Login URL:  https://stock.quicktiny.cn/login\n  Register:   https://stock.quicktiny.cn/register\n  Note:       \"openclaw skills已上线，懂的宝子们可以联系管理员啦～\"\n\nOpenClaw config:        /home/gem/workspace/agent/openclaw.json\n```\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: System: [2026-03-23 06:06:35 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0 [msg:om_x100b5332307964a0b31b7350c75c7f1]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5332307964a0b31b7350c75c7f1\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-23 06:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\"\n}\n```\n\n157990539@qq...\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): 登录后URL: https://stock.quicktiny.cn/ai\n页面内容(前500): openclaw skills已上线，懂的宝子们可以联系管理员啦～\n连板天梯\n行情信息\n连板天梯\n共识复盘\n自选股\n历史记录\n涨停基因\n题材库\n板块轮动\n涨停筛选\n短线周期\n可视化分析\n龙虎榜\n异动中心\n智能分析\n悟道\n问道\n量化实验室\n提示词广场\n个股分析\n晋级挑战\n多股对比\n热点资讯\n工具\n收起\n许\n市场分析\n智能梳理市场信息，洞察市场动态\nT5\n执行分析\nAI分析\n智能工具\n行情数据\n热点资讯\n其他\n全部23\n市场观察13\n经典模式5\n新闻催化3\n自定义2\n需求调查\n参与投票赢积分\nHot\n板块轮动\n四象限板块强弱分析\nNew\n题材库\nAI驱动的实时题材全景\nNew\n交割单归因\n交割单深度归因分析\n个股分析\n个股深度分析\n一图胜千言\n可视化全面复盘\n支持图表\n情绪温度计\n情绪周期判断\n主力资金战场\n解读主力资金动向\n支持图表\n明日市场分析\n分析明日看点\n支持图表\n20cm市场观察\n观察20cm标的\n龙头分析\n分析市场龙头\n支持图表\n1进2观察\n首板观察\n卡位分析\n卡位现象分析\n低吸大长腿\n波动特征观察\n超级挖掘机\n联网AI深度挖掘分析\n新闻催化龙头观察\n新闻催化龙头观察\n新闻催化\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): Command still running (session marine-sable, pid 304886). Use process (list/poll/log/write/kill/clear/remove) for follow-up.\n- Assistant: [non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (process): === 开发者页面 ===\nopenclaw skills已上线，懂的宝子们可以联系管理员啦～\n连板天梯\n行情信息\n连板天梯\n共识复盘\n自选股\n历史记录\n涨停基因\n题材库\n板块轮动\n涨停筛选\n短线周期\n可视化分析\n龙虎榜\n异动中心\n智能分析\n悟道\n问道\n量化实验室\n提示词广场\n个股分析\n晋级挑战\n多股对比\n热点资讯\n工具\n收起\n许\n