{"type":"message","id":"dfcc071c","parentId":"231773d9","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:23:30.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me provide the updated prediction with the sentiment cycle factored in. The market is in a \"退潮\" (retreat) phase with only 30 stocks hitting limit up on average recently. Let me recalculate with the sentiment adjustment.","thinkingSignature":"b27b54f4b1e39086df058542d82fa36facf8aaf0a28ab47343b01058540a31bd"},{"type":"text","text":"**【当前市场情绪周期判断】**\n\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 5日均值 | 30只/天 |\n| 10日均值 | 35只/天 |\n| 趋势 | 下降 |\n| **判断** | **退潮期** |\n\n**典型退潮特征（近5日）：**\n- 3/20（上周五）：仅25只涨停\n- 3/19（上周四）：仅21只涨停\n- 3/18（上周三）：反弹45只（短暂回暖）\n- 3/17（上周二）：仅25只\n- 3/16（上周一）：仅35只\n\n**退潮期规律：**\n- 涨停数量持续 < 50只/天\n- 连板股晋级率下降（跟风资金少）\n- 昨日涨停今日炸板率上升\n\n**校准后预测（退潮期 ×0.85）：**\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 板位 | 校准晋级% | 退潮调整后 | 竞价区间 |\n|------|------|------|-----------|-----------|----------|\n| 002310 | 东方新能 | 2板 | 40.2% | **34.2%** | 3~8% |\n| 603687 | 大胜达 | 3板 | 28.7% | **24.4%** | 1~6% |\n| 000601 | 韶能股份 | 3板 | 28.7% | **24.4%** | 1~6% |\n\n退潮期晋级概率打折后仍>20%的，仅剩东方新能(2板)、大胜达(3板)、韶能股份(3板)。首板股在退潮期晋级概率普遍偏低（<20%），需谨慎。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38893,"output":442,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69216,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774221800437}}
