{"type":"message","id":"c8a622d2","parentId":"9bdac01e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:26:09.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking which of the past 5 days was the \"node\" (节点) - i.e., a turning point or inflection point in the market. Looking at the data:\n\n- 2026-03-20: 25只 (low)\n- 2026-03-19: 21只 (very low, recent minimum)\n- 2026-03-18: 45只 (big jump from 21 to 45, +24) - this looks like a turning point\n- 2026-03-17: 25只 (drop from 45)\n- 2026-03-16: 35只\n\nThe pattern shows: 25 → 21 → 45 → 25 → 35\n\n\nThe sharp rebound from March 19 to March 18 stands out as the clearest inflection point, with the count jumping from 21 to 45 - that's a 24-stock increase marking the shift from low to elevated levels. March 20 then becomes the confirmation point where this elevated state validates the reversal.","thinkingSignature":"5d52b7e2299ee2b7288b865418404d5d1f84c381e79bc1c754309dd3062d423b"},{"type":"text","text":"看数据：\n\n| 日期 | 涨停数 | 变化 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| 03-16（周一） | 35只 | — |\n| 03-17（周二） | 25只 | ↓ |\n| 03-18（周三） | **45只** | **↑+20（爆发）** |\n| 03-19（周四） | 21只 | ↓↓（退潮确认） |\n| 03-20（周五） | 25只 | → 低位徘徊 |\n\n**节点是 03-18（周三）**\n\n逻辑：03-19 那天从45只骤降到21只，是退潮确认信号。前一天（03-18）的45只是**反弹高点**，随后立即被证伪——说明市场跟风资金不足，拉升后立即被获利了结。\n\n**节点日特征：**\n- 涨停数骤降 > 50%\n- 03-18 进的资金 → 03-19 大概率被埋\n- 随后连续3天维持 20-35 只低位\n\n**今日（周一）操作建议**：退潮确认后第一周，高板位（≥3板）谨慎，2板以下不接力，等情绪重新回暖再出手。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":478,"cacheRead":66935,"cacheWrite":2337,"totalTokens":69878,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774221953772}}
