{"type":"message","id":"f526cb2d","parentId":"f6662e6d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:33:24.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The output looks good. The system is now running. The sentiment analysis is integrated.\n\nKey findings:\n- Phase detected as \"启动期\" (startup phase) instead of \"退潮期\" (withdrawal)\n- Because: 5-day avg is 30 (right on the boundary), dt=13 (not >15), zt_dt_ratio=1.9 (>1)\n- The phase detection needs some adjustment - the threshold for 'withdraw' should be stricter\n\nLooking at the data again:\n- zt_avg = 30 (right on the boundary)\n- dt = 13 (not > 15, so not ice)\n\n\n- zt_dt_ratio = 1.9 (>1, so not withdraw by that criterion)\n\nThe detection logic is actually correct based on the current thresholds, but the thresholds themselves might be too lenient. With only 25-30 zt per day and dt stuck at 13-21, this feels more like a withdrawal phase. The issue is that my threshold for 'withdraw' is set too high at zt_max=30, when it should probably be lower to properly capture this pattern.\n\nLet me adjust the phase boundaries to be stricter: withdrawals should trigger at zt < 40 with dt >= 10, ice at zt < 25 with dt >= 15, and fermentation only when zt >= 50 and dt < 8. With the current readings, this would correctly classify it as withdrawal. The user's observation about market data seems accurate.","thinkingSignature":"e243ba83ea4e3905d6fa1679048d2e238f7e7b971da8b74fdff7745f5c39e478"},{"type":"text","text":"跑通了！发现一个问题——当前阶段判断为\"启动期\"，但根据网络资料和你观察到的实际情况，应该更接近\"退潮期\"。调整一下阈值：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zonecgvvy0ek_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/astock && python3 << 'EOF'\n# 实际数据验证阈值调整\n# 当前: 涨停均值30, 跌停13, 涨跌停比1.9\n# 严格标准: 涨停<40 + 跌停>10 → 退潮\n\n# 调整后判断\nzt_avg = 30\ndt = 13\nzt_dt_ratio = 1.9\n\n# 调整阈值\n# 退潮: zt_avg<40 and dt>10\n# 冰点: zt_avg<25 and dt>15\n# 发酵: zt_avg>=50 and dt<8\n\ndef detect(zt_avg, dt):\n    if zt_avg < 25 and dt > 15:\n        return '冰点', 0.4\n    if zt_avg < 40 and dt > 10:\n        return '退潮', 0.5\n    if zt_avg >= 50 and dt < 8:\n        return '高潮', 1.2\n    if zt_avg >= 40:\n        return '发酵', 1.0\n    return '启动', 0.7\n\nphase, coef = detect(zt_avg, dt)\nprint(f\"涨停均值: {zt_avg}, 跌停: {dt}\")\nprint(f\"判断: {phase}, 系数: ×{coef}\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48093,"output":669,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78643,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774222383232}}
