{"type":"message","id":"71b82cd0","parentId":"d33c1f27","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:40:34.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to integrate WeChat. This is a significant feature request. Let me think about what's involved.\n\nWeChat integration via OpenClaw would require:\n1. A WeChat channel plugin in OpenClaw\n2. The user needs to have WeChat connected to OpenClaw\n\nHowever, OpenClaw's channel plugins are typically for platforms that support bots/webhooks. WeChat official accounts have certain API capabilities, but personal WeChat (WeChat personal) is much harder to integrate because:\n- WeChat personal accounts don't have an official Bot API like Telegram or Discord\n- WeChat Work (企业微信) has some API capabilities\n\n\n- It would require the user to connect their WeChat account through OpenClaw's gateway\n\nLet me check the OpenClaw documentation to see what channels are actually supported.","thinkingSignature":"966df4562e889ccc8cfeda0e7628ebf514da10a0ee6d61f05a355f837f727087"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u4x9vrlsn8su_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw status 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":128,"output":202,"cacheRead":81929,"cacheWrite":878,"totalTokens":83137,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774222825245}}
