{"type":"message","id":"493d99a4","parentId":"5582a5e0","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:40:48.757Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9yzxl5leumwp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"bluebubbles.md\nbroadcast-groups.md\nchannel-routing.md\ndiscord.md\nfeishu.md\ngooglechat.md\ngroup-messages.md\ngroups.md\nimessage.md\nindex.md\nirc.md\nline.md\nlocation.md\nmatrix.md\nmattermost.md\nmsteams.md\nnextcloud-talk.md\nnostr.md\npairing.md\nsignal.md\nslack.md\nsynology-chat.md\ntelegram.md\ntlon.md\ntroubleshooting.md\ntwitch.md\nwhatsapp.md\nzalo.md\nzalouser.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"bluebubbles.md\nbroadcast-groups.md\nchannel-routing.md\ndiscord.md\nfeishu.md\ngooglechat.md\ngroup-messages.md\ngroups.md\nimessage.md\nindex.md\nirc.md\nline.md\nlocation.md\nmatrix.md\nmattermost.md\nmsteams.md\nnextcloud-talk.md\nnostr.md\npairing.md\nsignal.md\nslack.md\nsynology-chat.md\ntelegram.md\ntlon.md\ntroubleshooting.md\ntwitch.md\nwhatsapp.md\nzalo.md\nzalouser.md","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774222848746}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b7872e7","parentId":"493d99a4","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:40:59.277Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's no WeChat channel in OpenClaw's supported channels list. The available channels are: BlueBubbles, Discord, Feishu, GoogleChat, iMessage, IRC, Line, Matrix, Mattermost, MS Teams, Nostr, Signal, Slack, Synology Chat, Telegram, Twilio, Twitch, WhatsApp, Zalo.\n\nWeChat is NOT a supported channel. This means WeChat integration would require significant custom development or a plugin that doesn't exist.\n\nI should let the user know that WeChat is not natively supported by OpenClaw. WeChat personal accounts don't have a bot API - only WeChat Work (企业微信) has limited API capabilities, and even then it's complex.\n\n\nI should also flag that even if WeChat Work could be integrated, OpenClaw doesn't have built-in support for it, so it would require custom development work.","thinkingSignature":"31466a92c062fb58edcedee8804adf74b0c0079dc0d19ab150037d2669bd1079"},{"type":"text","text":"**微信不在 OpenClaw 支持的频道列表里。**\n\nOpenClaw 当前支持的频道：\n\n| 类别 | 平台 |\n|------|------|\n| 即时通讯 | Telegram、Signal、WhatsApp、iMessage、Line |\n| 办公协作 | 飞书、Slack、Microsoft Teams、Google Chat |\n| 社交 | Discord、Twitch |\n| 其他 | IRC、Matrix、Nostr |\n\n---\n\n**微信个人号**没有官方 Bot API，腾讯不开放个人微信的机器人接口，强行接入风险极高（容易封号）。\n\n**企业微信**有 API，但：\n1. OpenClaw 没有内置企业微信插件\n2. 接入复杂度高，需要企业认证和开发者配置\n\n---\n\n**替代方案：**\n\n| 方案 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **继续用飞书** | 当前已经跑通，所有功能都在飞书里 |\n| **接 Telegram** | 2分钟配置好，支持所有功能 |\n| **接微信群（企业微信）** | 需要额外开发，复杂度高 |\n\n如果想要多一个接收渠道，Telegram 是最简单的，5分钟搞定。要接吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":53505,"output":411,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774222848756}}
{"type":"message","id":"09322593","parentId":"7b7872e7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:41:01.050Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/8ca45c71-fed3-44e0-9ba6-082ce40591b9.jpg (image/jpeg) | /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/8ca45c71-fed3-44e0-9ba6-082ce40591b9.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-03-23 07:40:46 GMT+8] Exec completed (cool-wil, code 0) :: │ │ OS │ linux 6.8.0-100-generic (x64) · node 22.22.1 │ │ Tailscale │ off │ │ Channel │ stable (default) │\nSystem: [2026-03-23 07:41:00 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0 [msg:om_x100b533390378ca4b497d08c88ed4eb, image, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b533390378ca4b497d08c88ed4eb\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-23 07:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_12d595ebce7c7b73e926034c562b59d0\"\n}\n```\n\n/home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/8ca45c71-fed3-44e0-9ba6-082ce40591b9.jpg"}],"timestamp":1774222861043}}
