{"type":"message","id":"a6870933","parentId":"09f9c0a1","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:43:10.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The plugin was installed but it got terminated by SIGTERM. The process was waiting for the QR code scan. This makes sense - the process was waiting in the foreground for the user to scan the QR code with WeChat, but the exec tool has a timeout.\n\nThe issue is that this is a long-running interactive process - it needs the user to scan the QR code with their phone. This can't work in an exec background session because the user needs to scan the QR code.\n\nLet me think about what the user needs to do:\n1. The installation succeeded\n2. A QR code was displayed\n3. The user needs to scan it with their WeChat app\n4. But the process got killed because it was running in the background/exec\n\n\n5. The QR code was generated but only visible in the terminal output - the user never saw it since the exec command returned immediately\n\nI need to run this in the foreground so the user can actually scan the QR code with their phone.\n\nLet me execute it in the foreground with a longer timeout. Actually, I'm realizing the core issue - exec with pty=true provides an interactive terminal, so the QR code should render properly as ASCII art. But the real constraint is that the gateway might need to be restarted first for the plugin to load, and then the user needs to scan the QR code within that session before timeout. Let me try running this interactively and see if the WeChat plugin can be activated directly.","thinkingSignature":"440d09c1d97e73e3497955d0a4e7dd1fe4345ddc41305dded377bd762e63af14"},{"type":"text","text":"插件安装成功！二维码也生成了，但 exec 会话有时限。现在需要：\n\n**两步走：**\n\n**第一步**：重启 Gateway 加载插件\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i5ce51p6coap_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/openclaw-weixin/ 2>/dev/null && echo \"插件已安装\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58025,"output":379,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774222979044}}
