{"type":"message","id":"06f10c71","parentId":"c13a8ea5","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:43:15.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the plugin is installed. Now I need to restart the gateway to load the plugin. But after restart, the QR code scanning process needs to run interactively. The issue is that after gateway restart, the user needs to run the WeChat connection process interactively.\n\nLet me restart the gateway first, then help the user run the QR code scanning process.","thinkingSignature":"fb1acb7f747353924faf43cd6b40e183052a055ab3b95f5a547b2f7c1e3b5830"},{"type":"text","text":"插件在。但扫码连接需要交互式终端，我在前台跑，你用微信扫：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l4cz77mxs60b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sh /home/gem/workspace/agent/scripts/restart.sh 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58471,"output":142,"cacheRead":29881,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88494,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774222990650}}
