{"type":"message","id":"272972cd","parentId":"57416a28","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:04:18.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The WeChat plugin is in the allow list. The issue is that the WeChat channel is not configured in the `channels` section of openclaw.json. The `openclaw-weixin` plugin is loaded but not configured as a channel. Let me check how the plugin registers itself and what config is needed.\n\nActually, looking at the plugin's `openclaw.plugin.json`, it defines `\"channels\": [\"openclaw-weixin\"]`. So the channel should be auto-registered. But the channels config in openclaw.json only has `feishu`. I need to add the weixin channel config.\n\nLet me check what config the weixin channel needs.","thinkingSignature":"e5403bf6c481b927e2bc4ba5a8a6ab74d1686627ec7f2122d3807a4067f60ce1"},{"type":"text","text":"微信插件已加载但没有配置channel。需要添加channel配置：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zyf2bw7x5vsf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/gem/workspace/agent/extensions/openclaw-weixin/src/config/config-schema.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74382,"output":191,"cacheRead":29886,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774224250879}}
{"type":"message","id":"f535c072","parentId":"272972cd","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:04:18.148Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zyf2bw7x5vsf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { z } from \"zod\";\n\nimport { CDN_BASE_URL, DEFAULT_BASE_URL } from \"../auth/accounts.js\";\n\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// Zod config schema\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nconst weixinAccountSchema = z.object({\n  name: z.string().optional(),\n  enabled: z.boolean().optional(),\n  baseUrl: z.string().default(DEFAULT_BASE_URL),\n  cdnBaseUrl: z.string().default(CDN_BASE_URL),\n  routeTag: z.number().optional(),\n});\n\n/** Top-level weixin config schema (token is stored in credentials file, not config). */\nexport const WeixinConfigSchema = weixinAccountSchema.extend({\n  accounts: z.record(z.string(), weixinAccountSchema).optional(),\n  /** Default URL for `openclaw openclaw-weixin logs-upload`. Set via `openclaw config set channels.openclaw-weixin.logUploadUrl <url>`. */\n  logUploadUrl: z.string().optional(),\n});"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"import { z } from \"zod\";\n\nimport { CDN_BASE_URL, DEFAULT_BASE_URL } from \"../auth/accounts.js\";\n\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n// Zod config schema\n// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nconst weixinAccountSchema = z.object({\n  name: z.string().optional(),\n  enabled: z.boolean().optional(),\n  baseUrl: z.string().default(DEFAULT_BASE_URL),\n  cdnBaseUrl: z.string().default(CDN_BASE_URL),\n  routeTag: z.number().optional(),\n});\n\n/** Top-level weixin config schema (token is stored in credentials file, not config). */\nexport const WeixinConfigSchema = weixinAccountSchema.extend({\n  accounts: z.record(z.string(), weixinAccountSchema).optional(),\n  /** Default URL for `openclaw openclaw-weixin logs-upload`. Set via `openclaw config set channels.openclaw-weixin.logUploadUrl <url>`. */\n  logUploadUrl: z.string().optional(),\n});","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774224258131}}
